Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,So what was in the mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,邮件里有什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Peter Cuppin joined the Continentals.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,彼德库本加入独立军了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's 17, a year younger than l.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他才十七,比我还小一岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, the assembly's been convened, so l've been called to Charles Town.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,国民大会开会了 我被叫到查理士城去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-We're going to Charles Town? -We are.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我们要去查理士城? -对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We leave in the morning.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们明早就动身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aunt Charlotte!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,夏绿蒂阿姨!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Margaret, William, look at you.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,玛格莉特,威廉,看看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Missed you.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're huge. What have you been feeding them?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们长得好大,你给他们 吃了些什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:01.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, they're from good stock. On their mother's side, of course.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.57,0:09:01.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们的种好 因为是遗传自母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Come inside. Wait until you see what I have.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢,进来吧,我有 不少好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Presents? Presents for us? -Move slowly.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-给我们的礼物? -慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on these heathens, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们看好那些野蛮人,好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:26.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have this for you, Susan. It belonged to your mother.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.77,0:09:26.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我帮你准备了这个,苏珊 是你妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,She's still not talking?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她还是不开口?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It does me good to see you.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看到你,我的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Look, there's Gabriel.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看,那是佳百列
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hang King George!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,吊死乔治国王!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Death to King George!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,处死乔治国王!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Hang them all! -Hang the lot of them!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-把他们全都吊死! -一个都不要放过!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My name is Peter Howard.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是彼得霍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:20.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I lost most of my hearing and my left leg...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.70,0:10:20.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我丧失了大部份的听力和 我的左腿...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...fighting for the Crown in the French and lndian War.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...全都是为了 法国和印第安人之间的战事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And how did King George reward me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,乔治国王是怎么报答我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He cuts off my other leg with his taxes.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他用税废了我另一条腿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是你吗,霍华小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Howard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁,佳百列马汀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You know who I am, Gabriel Martin.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.51,0:10:42.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们最后一次见面我才11岁 你在我茶中加了墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:42.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The last time you saw me, I was 11 and you put ink in my tea.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.43,0:10:47.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那应该是我弟弟吧 也许是山缪或纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:47.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I believe that was one of my younger brothers. Perhaps Samuel or Nathan.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.14,0:10:52.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是你,那让我的牙齿 黑了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:52.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It was you, and it turned my teeth black for a month.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.86,0:10:59.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我们就给乔治国王 一个永生难忘的教训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:59.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and send a message to King George he will never forget!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的第一个议题...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Our first order of business...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也是最后的,让我们来投票 表决征兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And our last, if we vote a levy!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,安静...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Order, order!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,西门斯先生 你没有发言权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Simms, you do not have the floor.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,首先是哈利布尔上校 对独立军的演说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,First, an address by Colonel Harry Burwell of the Continental Army.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,布尔上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel Burwell.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大家都知道我为什么来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You all know why l'm here.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不是个演说家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not an orator.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我也不想说服大家 接受我们作战的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And I would not try to convince you of the worthiness of our cause.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是个军人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm a soldier.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And we are at war.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们在等宾州发表独立宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,From Philadelphia, we expect a declaration of independence.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,13个州中有8个州 都决定出资...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,8 of the 1 3 colonies have levied money...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...赞助独立军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...in support of a continental army.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我希望南卡能够成为第9个州
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I ask that South Carolina be the ninth.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,麻州和维吉尼亚州 也许在打仗...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Massachusetts and Virginia may be at war...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...但是南卡不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but South Carolina is not!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,赞成...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hear, hear.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.59,0:11:58.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这一场战争不是为了争取 一,两个州的独立...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:58.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is not a war for the independence of one or two colonies...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...而是争取整个国家的独立
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but for the independence of one nation.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,哪个国家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And what nation is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,美国!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,An American nation!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没有这个国家,这么说是叛国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There is no such nation and to speak of one is treason.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们是美国的国民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We are citizens of an American nation.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的权利却受到三千英哩外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And our rights are being threatened...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...暴君的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...by a tyrant 3000 miles away.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,霍华先生,请告诉我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me, please, Mr. Howard...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我为什么要用 三千哩外的暴君...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...why should I trade one tyrant 3000 miles away...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...来换一英哩外的 三千个暴君?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...for 3000 tyrants one mile away?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.29,0:12:36.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,民选国会也能像国王一样 践踏我们的人权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:36.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,An elected legislature can trample a man's rights as easily as a king can.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,马汀上尉...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Captain Martin...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我知道你很爱国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I understood you to be a patriot.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想知道我是否因遭课重税 而愤愤不平?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If you mean by "patriot," am I angry about taxation without representation?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的,我很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, I am.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,美国是否该独立自主?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Should the American colonies govern themselves independently?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我认为他们可以也应该
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I believe they can. And they should.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.48,0:13:01.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但若你问我 是否该跟英国宣战...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:01.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But if you're asking me am I willing to go to war with England...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我的答覆是否定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...then the answer is most definitely no.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,难道这就是在英法战争时...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This from the same Captain Benjamin Martin whose fury was so famous...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,怒气勃发的马汀上尉说的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...during the Wilderness campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I was intemperate in my youth.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,当年我年少轻狂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Temperance can be a disguise for fear.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,节制很可能是恐惧的伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Middleton, I fought with Captain Martin...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,米德顿先生 我和马汀上尉...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...under Washington in the French and lndian War.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...一起在华盛顿将军的 麾下打过仗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There's not a man in this room...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这屋里没有任何人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:33.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...or anywhere for that matter, to whom I would more willingly trust my life.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.35,0:13:33.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...比他还值得我信任的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There are alternatives to war.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,除了战争还有别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We take our case before the king.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以向国王陈情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-We plead with him. -We tried.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我们可以跟他讲理 -我们试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, then, we try again and again if necessary to avoid a war.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那么,我们应一试再试 极力避免战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I was at Bunker Hill.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我参加过邦克山之役
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The British advanced three times.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,英军推进了三次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We killed 700 at point-blank range and still they took the ground.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们近距离杀了七百名英军 但他们仍然攻下邦克山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That is the measure of their resolve.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是他们解决的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If your principles dictate independence...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你的原则是坚持独立...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...then war is the only way.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...那唯有作战一途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It is come to that.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战争是无法避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hear, hear.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,对...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have seven children.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我有七个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My wife is dead.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,内人已死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Now, who's to care for them if I go to war?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我去作战谁来照顾他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Wars are not fought only by childless men.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不光是没有小孩的男人 才去作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Granted.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But mark my words.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但请记下我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:37.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This war will be fought, not on the frontier...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.74,0:14:37.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这场战争将不是在前线进行...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...or on some distant battlefield...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...也不是在遥远的战场...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but amongst us.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...战火会在身边燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Among our homes.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在我们的家中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Our children will learn of it with their own eyes.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的孩子们 将会亲身体验战争的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And the innocent will die with the rest of us.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们的童真 将会和我们一起死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I will not fight.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不参战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And because I will not fight, I will not cast a vote...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,正因为如此 我不打算参与投票...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...that will send others to fight in my stead.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...将别人送上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And your principles?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你的原则呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm a parent. I haven't got the luxury of principles.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是有孩子的人 我没有讲原则的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We must vote to levy!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们一定要投票赞成征兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,28 to 1 2! The levy passed!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,28比12!征兵通过了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You intend to enlist without my permission?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你打算擅自入伍?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:30.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father, I thought you were a man of principle.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.48,0:16:30.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲,我还以为 你是个有原则的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When you have a family of your own, perhaps you'll understand.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你有家室后自会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When I have a family of my own, I won't hide behind them.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我有家室也不会用他们 来当挡箭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's as imprudent as his father was at his age.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他像他父亲小时候一样鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Regrettably so.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it that he serves under me.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会尽量将他 收在我的羽翼之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:15.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Make him a clerk or quartermaster, something of that sort.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.23,0:17:15.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我叫他去做文官或补给官之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Thomas: Though many seasons have passed...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的汤玛斯： 虽然过了许多年...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:51.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...it seems like only yesterday when we last saw each other in Charles Town.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.02,0:17:51.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...但在查理士城见面 彷彿是昨日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:55.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,With sadness, I learned of its recent fall to the British...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.94,0:17:55.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很遗憾听说英军在 康瓦理斯将军的指挥下...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...under General Cornwallis.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...打败我们的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I received a letter from Aunt Charlotte...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我今天接到 夏绿蒂阿姨的信...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...saying she closed her home in Charles Town after the city fell...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...告诉我她在 查理士城沦陷后锁上家门...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and moved to her plantation on the Santee.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...然后搬到 山提河畔的农场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Here in the north, our campaign has been marked by defeat and privation.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在北边我们弹尽粮绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Our losses have been grievous.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们伤亡惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:39.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My good friend, Peter Cuppin, fell at Elizabethtown.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.90,0:18:39.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的好友彼德库本 在伊莉莎白镇战死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,His death has been difficult to bear.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他的死讯让我伤痛欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We will march south with General Gates...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们即将和 盖兹将军南进...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...to fight the Redcoats under Cornwallis.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...和康瓦理斯将军的 红衫军对决
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Easy, Red. Easy.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢来...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I envy you...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我羡慕你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:31.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...your youth and distance from this cruel conflict of which I am a part.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.87,0:19:31.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我羡慕你和战争毫无瓜葛 而我却是这场战争的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,"But I am fortunate to be serving the cause of Liberty.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但我觉得自己有幸 能够为自由而战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And though I fear death...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,虽然我畏惧死亡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...each day in prayer I reaffirm my willingness...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...但每天我都祈祷 我在必要时...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...to give my life in its service.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...能为自由捐躯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Pray for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为我祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But above all, pray for the cause.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为争取自由而祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your loving brother, Gabriel."
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,爱你的哥哥,佳百列上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:30.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.77,0:20:30.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,转身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not yet, Thomas.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在还不行,汤玛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,等你17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's two years. It's already been two.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那还要两年,我已经等了两年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-The war could be over by then. -God willing.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-到时战争说不定结束了 -老天保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Seventeen.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,17岁就17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Put it back, please.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,请放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What happened at Fort Wilderness?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,威尔德尼斯堡 发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Put it away.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,收好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Six-pounders.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,六磅炮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Lots of them.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How far away?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,有多远?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:14.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're a long way off. They're most likely heading the other direction.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.20,0:22:14.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还远着呢 看来是瞄准别的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Put those in the house.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把枪收进去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-They might come this way. -Must I tell you again?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-他们可能朝着这里来 -要我再说一遍吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Let's all stay close in to the house, all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们全躲在家里,懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We'll have to fight them off.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们要赶走英军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Won't Father do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲不会这么做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'll probably kill us men...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们也许会杀了我们男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and do Lord-knows-what to you women.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...凌虐你们女生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nathan!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,纳森!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:27.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Slowly turn.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.36,0:23:27.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Abigale!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,艾比佳!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Water and bandages, fast.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,快去拿水和绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The battle. Were you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.29,0:23:46.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你有在作战现场吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:48.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Have you seen any Redcoats?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.67,0:23:48.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你有看见红衫军吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Abigale, the children, please.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,艾比佳,快去照顾孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Children, come. Upstairs.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们,跟我上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gates marched us straight at the Redcoats.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,盖兹带着我们直捣红衫军黄龙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:07.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Our lines broke. The British Green Dragoons cut us to bits.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:03.81,0:24:07.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的防线失散了 被英军打得溃不成军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:10.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I was given these dispatches.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:07.82,0:24:10.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上级给我这些急件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:14.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As I left, I saw the Virginia Regulars surrender.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.49,0:24:14.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我离开时看到 维吉尼亚正规军投降
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:19.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The Dragoons rode into them.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.49,0:24:19.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,英军长驱直入
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:22.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Killed them all.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:21.16,0:24:22.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把他们杀光了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:25.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Over 200 men.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:23.50,0:24:25.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,两百多个人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:28.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have to get these dispatches to Hillsborough.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:26.59,0:24:28.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我一定要把这些急件 送到西尔斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.42,0:24:29.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You can't ride.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.42,0:24:29.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你不能骑马
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:32.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here! It's not safe for...
Dialogue: 1,0:24:29.80,0:24:32.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不能留在这! 我在这里会危及...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.38,0:25:06.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:25:05.38,0:25:06.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,发火!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:16.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:25:15.22,0:25:16.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:58.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the care of His Majesty's soldiers.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:56.19,0:26:58.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们照顾国王的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.89,0:27:32.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Have a detachment take our wounded to our surgeons at Winnsboro.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:29.89,0:27:32.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,中尉,派一队人马 送我们的伤兵去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:34.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:33.40,0:27:34.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.36,0:27:37.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire the house and barns.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:36.36,0:27:37.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,放火烧了那栋房子和谷仓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:43.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Let it be known if you harbor the enemy you will lose your home.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:40.03,0:27:43.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们要是敢窝藏敌军 就会无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:49.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,By order of King George...
Dialogue: 1,0:27:47.29,0:27:49.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,乔治国王有令...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.37,0:27:52.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...all slaves of the American colonies who fight for the Crown...
Dialogue: 1,0:27:49.37,0:27:52.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...任何只要为英国效力的 美国奴隶...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:56.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will be granted their freedom with our victory.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:53.04,0:27:56.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...只要我们战胜 就能成为自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.42,0:28:02.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We're not slaves. We work this land. We're freedmen.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:58.42,0:28:02.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们不是奴隶,我们只是 在这里工作,我们是自由人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:05.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Then you're freedmen who will have the privilege...
Dialogue: 1,0:28:02.22,0:28:05.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那各位就是有幸为...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.51,0:28:07.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...of fighting in the king's army.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:05.51,0:28:07.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...英国军队效力的自由人了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.65,0:28:15.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Rebel dispatches, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:13.65,0:28:15.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,敌军的快递,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.90,0:28:23.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Who carried this?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:21.90,0:28:23.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是谁的?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.54,0:28:33.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Who carried this?!
Dialogue: 1,0:28:32.54,0:28:33.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谁的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.67,0:28:35.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I did, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:34.67,0:28:35.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.51,0:28:44.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I was wounded. These people gave me care.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:42.51,0:28:44.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我受伤了,这些人照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.51,0:28:47.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They have nothing to do with the dispatches.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:45.51,0:28:47.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们和这些密令没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.85,0:28:52.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take this one to Camden. He is a spy.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:50.85,0:28:52.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,带他去坎登,他是间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:55.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hang him, put his body on display.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:52.94,0:28:55.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,吊死他,尸首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.61,0:28:57.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's a dispatch rider.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:55.61,0:28:57.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他是个传令兵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.73,0:29:00.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Destroy the livestock. Save the horses for the Dragoons.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:57.73,0:29:00.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,杀了活口把马留给英军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.15,0:29:04.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel, this is a uniformed dispatch rider carrying a marked case.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:01.15,0:29:04.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上校他是带着密令的 制服传令兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:06.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He cannot be held as a spy.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:05.20,0:29:06.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他不能被视为间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.74,0:29:09.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, we won't hold him. We're going to hang him.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:06.74,0:29:09.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们不打算关他 我们要吊死他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.04,0:29:14.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Colonel... -Father!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:13.04,0:29:14.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-上校... -父亲!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.00,0:29:20.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. He's your son.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:18.00,0:29:20.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我懂了,他是你儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.96,0:29:24.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should've taught him something of loyalty.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:21.96,0:29:24.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许你该教他什么叫做爱国
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:30.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel, I beg you, please reconsider. By the rules of war...
Dialogue: 1,0:29:26.14,0:29:30.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上校,我求你 根据作战时的规定...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.60,0:29:34.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Would you like a lesson, sir, in the rules of war?
Dialogue: 1,0:29:30.60,0:29:34.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你想知道 什么叫作战规则吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.23,0:29:38.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps your children would.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:37.23,0:29:38.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许你的小孩想上一课
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.95,0:29:45.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No lesson is necessary.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:43.95,0:29:45.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,无此必要
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.66,0:29:49.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:48.66,0:29:49.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.87,0:29:51.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What of the rebel wounded?
Dialogue: 1,0:29:49.87,0:29:51.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那些受伤的叛军怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.16,0:29:55.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:54.16,0:29:55.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.38,0:30:01.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:00.38,0:30:01.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.68,0:30:07.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father, do something!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:05.68,0:30:07.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲,快想想办法!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,安静!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.52,0:30:23.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel, run!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:21.52,0:30:23.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.53,0:30:25.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:24.53,0:30:25.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.41,0:30:29.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:28.41,0:30:29.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.02,0:30:57.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stupid boy.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:56.02,0:30:57.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.90,0:31:05.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:03.90,0:31:05.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.09,0:32:08.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Come, child.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:07.09,0:32:08.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,来吧,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.30,0:32:12.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving these children!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:10.30,0:32:12.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-不! -我不会留下这些孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.93,0:32:14.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mercy!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:12.93,0:32:14.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,手下留情!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.64,0:32:17.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:15.64,0:32:17.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.31,0:32:18.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Present!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:17.31,0:32:18.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,举枪!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.52,0:32:19.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:18.52,0:32:19.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.77,0:33:05.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All of you, stay here.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:03.77,0:33:05.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们都留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.64,0:33:42.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nathan, Samuel.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:40.64,0:33:42.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,纳森,山缪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.90,0:33:48.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Margaret.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:46.90,0:33:48.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,玛格莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.57,0:33:53.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hide in the fields with William and Susan.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:50.57,0:33:53.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要你们带着威廉和苏珊 躲在田里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.32,0:33:56.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If we're not back by sunset, take them to Aunt Charlotte's.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:53.32,0:33:56.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们黄昏时没有回来 就带他们去找夏绿蒂阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.24,0:33:57.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:56.24,0:33:57.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,懂了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.33,0:34:00.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Boys.
Dialogue: 1,0:33:59.33,0:34:00.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's a good spot.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这个地点不错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.42,0:34:58.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Boys, listen to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:56.42,0:34:58.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.09,0:35:00.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll fire first.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:59.09,0:35:00.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我先开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.89,0:35:05.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Start with the officers and work your way down.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:02.89,0:35:05.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要你们先开枪打军官 再打士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.98,0:35:07.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Can you tell the difference?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:05.98,0:35:07.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们知道哪些是军官吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.94,0:35:08.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:07.94,0:35:08.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,知道,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.14,0:35:10.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Yes, Father. -Good.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:09.14,0:35:10.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-知道 -很好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.56,0:35:14.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Samuel, after your first shot, reload for Nathan.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:11.56,0:35:14.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,山缪,在你开第一枪后 就帮纳森装子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.28,0:35:16.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 1,0:35:15.28,0:35:16.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.49,0:35:19.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...if anything should happen to me, drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:16.49,0:35:19.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...万一我有个三长两短 我要你们放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.49,0:35:21.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Run as quickly as you can.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:19.49,0:35:21.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,能跑多快就跑多快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:23.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Get your brother and your sisters...
Dialogue: 1,0:35:21.32,0:35:23.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,回家去找弟弟,妹妹...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.99,0:35:26.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and take them to Aunt Charlotte's. Understood?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:23.99,0:35:26.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...带他们去夏绿蒂阿姨家 懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:29.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What did I say about shooting?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:28.33,0:35:29.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还记得我教你们怎么开枪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.50,0:35:31.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aim small, miss small.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:30.50,0:35:31.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄小目标失误就少
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:33.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aim small, miss small.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:32.25,0:35:33.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄小目标失误就少
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.13,0:35:36.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Boys...
Dialogue: 1,0:35:35.13,0:35:36.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,孩子们...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.84,0:35:38.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...Samuel...
Dialogue: 1,0:35:36.84,0:35:38.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...山缪...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.55,0:35:39.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...steady.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:38.55,0:35:39.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.39,0:36:29.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Lord, make me fast and accurate.
Dialogue: 1,0:36:27.39,0:36:29.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上帝,保佑我又快又准
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.39,0:36:33.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aim small, miss small.
Dialogue: 1,0:36:31.39,0:36:33.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄小目标失误就少
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.06,0:36:36.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aim small, miss small.
Dialogue: 1,0:36:34.06,0:36:36.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄小目标失误就少
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.07,0:36:39.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aim small, miss small.
Dialogue: 1,0:36:37.07,0:36:39.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄小目标失误就少
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.54,0:36:55.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-On the right! -To the left!
Dialogue: 1,0:36:53.54,0:36:55.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-上面,在右边! -在左边!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.34,0:37:03.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Behind us! Up on the ridge!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:01.34,0:37:03.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在后面!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:09.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Form right!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:07.89,0:37:09.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,从右边来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.27,0:37:12.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To the right!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:11.27,0:37:12.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,右转!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.35,0:37:15.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,About face!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:14.35,0:37:15.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,向后转!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.61,0:37:20.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,On the right to the rear!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:18.61,0:37:20.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在右边的山上!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.24,0:37:22.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To the right!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:21.24,0:37:22.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,向右转!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.41,0:37:27.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Reload! -Reload!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:25.41,0:37:27.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-装子弹! -装子弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.68,0:37:48.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:46.68,0:37:48.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在后面!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.98,0:37:54.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Look on the rear!
Dialogue: 1,0:37:52.98,0:37:54.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,注意后面!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.13,0:41:15.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We have the private the Cherokee scouts brought in.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:13.13,0:41:15.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们印地安斥候 带回来的二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:19.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Private?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:17.85,0:41:19.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,二等兵?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.39,0:41:20.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Private.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:19.39,0:41:20.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.64,0:41:22.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel William Tavington, Green Dragoons.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:20.64,0:41:22.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是青龙部队的 威廉塔维顿上校
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.48,0:41:25.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What happened? Who did this?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:23.48,0:41:25.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了?谁干的好事?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:27.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Him.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:26.73,0:41:27.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:30.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It was mad.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.19,0:41:30.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,当时情况一团乱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you who it was.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我也说不上来是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.32,0:41:35.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Calm down, man.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:33.32,0:41:35.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,冷静点...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.03,0:41:38.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Twenty of His Majesty's soldiers are dead.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:36.03,0:41:38.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们损失了20名皇家士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.03,0:41:41.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And I need to know how.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:39.03,0:41:41.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.70,0:41:43.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-He said there was... -Were you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:41.70,0:41:43.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-他说有... -你在场吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.29,0:41:46.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Then let him speak.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:44.29,0:41:46.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那就让他说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:50.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take your time and tell me. How many were there?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:47.04,0:41:50.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢来 告诉我有多少人?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.63,0:41:52.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Were they militia? Were they Regulars?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:50.63,0:41:52.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是民兵吗?还是正规军?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.05,0:41:55.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember how many.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:53.05,0:41:55.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不记得有多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.76,0:41:58.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe one.
Dialogue: 1,0:41:57.76,0:41:58.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.14,0:42:03.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,One man. Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:42:01.14,0:42:03.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一个人,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.89,0:42:05.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He was in the flank.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:03.89,0:42:05.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他在侧面攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.15,0:42:08.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All around us.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:07.15,0:42:08.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,似乎在我们周边游走
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.11,0:42:10.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Amongst us.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:09.11,0:42:10.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,又彷彿在我们之间
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.40,0:42:13.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I could barely see him. He was there, then he was gone.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:11.40,0:42:13.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他来无影去无踪 我几乎看不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.99,0:42:15.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He just vanished.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:13.99,0:42:15.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他就这样消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.86,0:42:19.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sounds more like a ghost than a man.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:16.86,0:42:19.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,听起来像鬼不像人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.57,0:42:21.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A ghost.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:19.57,0:42:21.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.58,0:42:24.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He was like a ghost.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:22.58,0:42:24.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他是很像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.91,0:42:27.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:25.91,0:42:27.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.38,0:42:32.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Bordon? Take a patrol.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:29.38,0:42:32.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,波顿?带一队侦察队
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.25,0:42:35.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Capture this ghost before word of his exploits spread.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:32.25,0:42:35.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看看能不能在消息传开之前 抓到这个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.47,0:42:38.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Who's this? -Sir, this is Captain Wilkins.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:35.47,0:42:38.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-这是谁? -他是威尔金上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.59,0:42:42.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He was with the Loyalist Colonial Militia. He might be of use.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:38.59,0:42:42.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他曾经是英国民兵 说不定派得上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.60,0:42:44.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Another colonial.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:42.60,0:42:44.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,又一个殖民地居民
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.89,0:42:47.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Captain Wilkins, where do your loyalties lie?
Dialogue: 1,0:42:44.89,0:42:47.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,威尔金上尉,你忠于哪一方?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.60,0:42:48.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To king and country.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:47.60,0:42:48.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我忠于英王和祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.10,0:42:51.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Why should I trust a man who'd betray his neighbors?
Dialogue: 1,0:42:49.10,0:42:51.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我为什么要信任一个 出卖邻居的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.36,0:42:55.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Those neighbors of mine who stand against England...
Dialogue: 1,0:42:52.36,0:42:55.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我那些出卖英国的邻居...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.61,0:42:57.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...deserve to die a traitor's death.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:55.61,0:42:57.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...罪该万死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.45,0:42:59.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:58.45,0:42:59.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,咱们走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.79,0:43:07.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Martin!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:05.79,0:43:07.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,马汀先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.63,0:43:15.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Charlotte!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:13.63,0:43:15.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,夏绿蒂小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.89,0:43:29.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You're safe now. Try to sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:26.89,0:43:29.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们安全了,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.90,0:43:31.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:29.90,0:43:31.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.48,0:43:32.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:31.48,0:43:32.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.32,0:43:34.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:33.32,0:43:34.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.82,0:43:36.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:34.82,0:43:36.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.99,0:43:39.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I killed those men.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:36.99,0:43:39.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我杀了那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.41,0:43:41.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You did what I told you to do.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:40.41,0:43:41.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你只是照我的话去做
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.33,0:43:46.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You did what you had to. There was no wrong in it.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:43.33,0:43:46.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那是你该做的 这没什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.96,0:43:51.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I killed them.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:48.96,0:43:51.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.63,0:43:56.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:54.63,0:43:56.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.01,0:44:07.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:06.01,0:44:07.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.21,0:44:40.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing for which you should be ashamed.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:37.21,0:44:40.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你做了没什么好觉得 羞耻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.43,0:44:44.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I've done nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:42.43,0:44:44.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.80,0:44:47.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And for that, I am ashamed.
Dialogue: 1,0:44:45.80,0:44:47.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,所以我很羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.28,0:45:08.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gates and the Continental Army are at Hillsborough.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:06.28,0:45:08.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,盖兹和独立军在席尔斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.45,0:45:10.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm joining up with them.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:09.45,0:45:10.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要去加入他们
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.13,0:45:18.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No. Your place is here now.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:16.13,0:45:18.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不,你得留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.38,0:45:20.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm going back. I'm a soldier, it's my duty.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:18.38,0:45:20.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要回去,我是个军人 这是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.46,0:45:23.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your duty is to your family.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:21.46,0:45:23.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你要对你的家庭负责
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.14,0:45:27.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Don't you walk away from me, boy!
Dialogue: 1,0:45:25.14,0:45:27.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不准你弃我于不顾!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.30,0:45:28.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll find you when it's over.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:27.30,0:45:28.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战争结束后我会来找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.81,0:45:30.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, I forbid you to go!
Dialogue: 1,0:45:28.81,0:45:30.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不准你去!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.81,0:45:33.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-l'm not a child! -You're my child!
Dialogue: 1,0:45:30.81,0:45:33.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我不是个小孩! -你是我的小孩!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.31,0:45:37.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Father.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:36.31,0:45:37.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.98,0:45:42.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thomas is dead.
Dialogue: 1,0:45:40.98,0:45:42.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,汤玛斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How many more have to die before you'll heed my word?
Dialogue: 1,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,到底要死多少人 你才会注意听我的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.14,0:46:18.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my family.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:16.14,0:46:18.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我在失去我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.98,0:46:24.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When will you be back, Father?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:21.98,0:46:24.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲,你什么时候会回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.03,0:46:26.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:25.03,0:46:26.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.82,0:46:28.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:46:26.82,0:46:28.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,明天吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.53,0:46:30.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, not tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:28.53,0:46:30.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.78,0:46:32.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You say your prayers.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:30.78,0:46:32.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,乖乖祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.79,0:46:33.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:32.79,0:46:33.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.70,0:46:38.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take care of your brothers and sisters and your Aunt Charlotte.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:34.70,0:46:38.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,照顾弟弟,妹妹和夏绿蒂阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.71,0:46:40.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:38.71,0:46:40.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.38,0:46:43.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As I am on you, Samuel.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:41.38,0:46:43.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还有你,山缪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.80,0:46:45.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:44.80,0:46:45.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.81,0:46:54.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Susan...
Dialogue: 1,0:46:52.81,0:46:54.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,苏珊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.39,0:46:57.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...goodbye.
Dialogue: 1,0:46:56.39,0:46:57.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.45,0:47:13.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:47:12.45,0:47:13.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.79,0:49:23.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 1,0:49:21.79,0:49:23.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.54,0:49:29.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Make ready!
Dialogue: 1,0:49:27.54,0:49:29.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.97,0:49:35.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 1,0:49:33.97,0:49:35.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄准!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.10,0:49:41.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:49:40.10,0:49:41.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.36,0:49:55.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:53.36,0:49:55.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.82,0:49:58.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't expect you would.
Dialogue: 1,0:49:55.82,0:49:58.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我也没有指望你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.58,0:50:04.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That Gates is a damn fool.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:02.58,0:50:04.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那个盖兹是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.83,0:50:09.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He spent too many years in the British army.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:06.83,0:50:09.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他在英国部队混了太久
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:13.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Going muzzle-to-muzzle with Redcoats in open field. It's madness.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:09.50,0:50:13.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,居然想在旷野中击败红衫军 真疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.22,0:50:15.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:14.22,0:50:15.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.80,0:50:17.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Make ready!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:15.80,0:50:17.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.14,0:50:19.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Present!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:18.14,0:50:19.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,举枪!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.01,0:50:22.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:21.01,0:50:22.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.04,0:50:47.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This battle was over before it began.
Dialogue: 1,0:50:45.04,0:50:47.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这场战争在开始前就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.34,0:50:58.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:57.34,0:50:58.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.26,0:51:01.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.26,0:51:01.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.10,0:51:10.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These rustics are so inept.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:08.10,0:51:10.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这些乡巴佬真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.11,0:51:13.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nearly takes the honor out of victory.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:11.11,0:51:13.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,差点害我们赢的毫无光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.44,0:51:15.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nearly.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:14.44,0:51:15.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.20,0:51:22.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hold him firm.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:21.20,0:51:22.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,压住他
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.47,0:51:43.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Where's your commanding officer? -That tent there.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:40.47,0:51:43.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-你们的指挥官呢? -在那个帐篷里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.14,0:51:51.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's a lost cause.
Dialogue: 1,0:51:50.14,0:51:51.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那是个失败的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.75,0:52:10.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin Martin.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:08.75,0:52:10.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明马汀
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.54,0:52:12.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm in no mood for a lecture.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:10.54,0:52:12.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不想听训
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.83,0:52:15.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where's your General Gates now?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:12.83,0:52:15.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们的盖兹将军呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.55,0:52:19.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The last anyone saw, riding hard northeast...
Dialogue: 1,0:52:15.55,0:52:19.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,有人看到他骑着马 朝东南方走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.92,0:52:22.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...his staff 100 yards behind, trying to catch up.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:19.92,0:52:22.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...他的属下在百码后苦苦追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.68,0:52:25.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,So who's in command?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:23.68,0:52:25.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在由谁指挥?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.01,0:52:27.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:26.01,0:52:27.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.31,0:52:29.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:28.31,0:52:29.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.85,0:52:32.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What are my orders?
Dialogue: 1,0:52:30.85,0:52:32.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你要下什么命令给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.19,0:52:40.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We're a breath away from losing this war, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:37.19,0:52:40.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明,我们差一口气 就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.20,0:52:46.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,In the north, Washington is reeling from Morristown.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:43.20,0:52:46.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,华盛顿在莫瑞斯镇重整军备
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.45,0:52:49.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's running and hiding from 12,000 Redcoats.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:46.45,0:52:49.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他在躲一万两千名红衫军
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.33,0:52:51.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,In the south, Cornwallis has broken our back.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:49.33,0:52:51.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们在南方的军队 又被康瓦理斯打得溃不成军
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.12,0:52:55.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Captured over 5000 of our troops when he took Charles Town.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:52.12,0:52:55.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他攻陷查理士城时 俘掳了我们五千名弟兄
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.59,0:52:58.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And he destroyed the only army between him and New York.
Dialogue: 1,0:52:55.59,0:52:58.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他也击溃了唯一挡在 他和纽约间的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.47,0:53:03.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing will stop him from heading north to finish off Washington.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:00.47,0:53:03.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们根本无力阻挡他 长驱直入击败华盛顿的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.09,0:53:08.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Unless we can keep Cornwallis in the south till the French arrive.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:04.09,0:53:08.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,除非我们想办法把康瓦理斯 留在南方,直到法军抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:12.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They've promised a fleet and 10,000 troops.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:09.10,0:53:12.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们答应要派一支舰队 和一千名士兵来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.23,0:53:13.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:12.23,0:53:13.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,何时?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.94,0:53:17.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Six months at the earliest.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:14.94,0:53:17.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,最快还要六个月
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.57,0:53:19.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You trust the French to keep their word?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:17.57,0:53:19.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你相信法国人会言而有信?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.15,0:53:21.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Absolument.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:20.15,0:53:21.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.78,0:53:26.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin Martin. Major Jean Villeneuve.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:23.78,0:53:26.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明马汀 这位是维伦少校
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.74,0:53:29.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,French Seventh Light Foot. He will help train the militia.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:26.74,0:53:29.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他是法国第七步兵连的 他来帮我们训练民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.29,0:53:33.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The hero of Fort Wilderness. Your reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:30.29,0:53:33.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你是维尔德尼斯的英雄 久仰了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.46,0:53:41.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You really expect to hold Cornwallis here using just militia?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:38.46,0:53:41.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你真的想用民兵 来阻止康瓦理斯推进?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.88,0:53:44.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not me. You.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:41.88,0:53:44.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不是我,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.43,0:53:48.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're not soldiers, they're farmers.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:46.43,0:53:48.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,哈利,他们不是军人,是农民
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.85,0:53:51.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'd be better off letting the British march through.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:48.85,0:53:51.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,让英军通过对他们比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.43,0:53:54.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'd be better off, but the cause wouldn't.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:51.43,0:53:54.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没错,但形势不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.14,0:53:57.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How many men does Cornwallis have?
Dialogue: 1,0:53:55.14,0:53:57.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,康瓦理斯手下有多少人?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.61,0:53:59.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,8000 infantry.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:57.61,0:53:59.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,八千名步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.90,0:54:02.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Around 600 cavalry.
Dialogue: 1,0:53:59.90,0:54:02.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,六百名骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.49,0:54:05.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you a field commission as a colonel.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:02.49,0:54:05.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我任命你为上校
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.49,0:54:08.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Might I request that you transfer my son under my command?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:05.49,0:54:08.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,长官,可以把我儿子 派到我的部队吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.57,0:54:09.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir, no, l...
Dialogue: 1,0:54:08.57,0:54:09.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,长官,不,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.12,0:54:11.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's done.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:10.12,0:54:11.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.91,0:54:16.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:14.91,0:54:16.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.08,0:54:20.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel, l've been a soldier for two years.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:18.08,0:54:20.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上校,我已经当了两年兵
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.21,0:54:22.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As a scout, horseman, marksman, scavenger.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:20.21,0:54:22.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我当过斥候骑兵,狙击兵 清道兵
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.92,0:54:25.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-ls that so? -l'd be of better use with Regulars.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:22.92,0:54:25.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-是吗? -我在正规军比较有发展
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.68,0:54:27.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where'd you learn all that riding, shooting, scavenging?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:25.68,0:54:27.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你是从哪儿学会骑马 开枪的?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.01,0:54:29.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My father taught me.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:28.01,0:54:29.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是我父亲教的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.64,0:54:33.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Teach you any humility?
Dialogue: 1,0:54:31.64,0:54:33.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他有没有教你如何谦虚?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.93,0:54:35.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He tried. It didn't take.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:33.93,0:54:35.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他试过,但我不受教
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.98,0:54:40.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He also taught you every trail between here and Charles Town...
Dialogue: 1,0:54:36.98,0:54:40.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他也教你认从这儿 到查理士城的每一条小路...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.82,0:54:42.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...which is why he transferred you.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:40.82,0:54:42.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...所以才会把你调过来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.28,0:54:45.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We'll put the word out. Start on the south side of...
Dialogue: 1,0:54:43.28,0:54:45.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们放话出去 我们从山提河南岸开始...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.11,0:54:48.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We'll cover more ground if we split up.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:46.11,0:54:48.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,分头进行比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.95,0:54:55.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well, corporal. You take Harrisville, Pembroke, Wakefield.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:51.95,0:54:55.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很好,下士,你去哈利斯维尔 潘布克,维克菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.66,0:54:59.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll start on the north side. Meet at the mission in Black Swamp.
Dialogue: 1,0:54:55.66,0:54:59.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我从北边开始,到黑沼泽会合
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.84,0:55:04.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Corporal.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:03.84,0:55:04.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,下士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.72,0:55:08.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:06.72,0:55:08.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.47,0:55:11.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:10.47,0:55:11.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.64,0:55:18.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You have children?
Dialogue: 1,0:55:16.64,0:55:18.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你有孩子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.86,0:55:24.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,French.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:22.86,0:55:24.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,法国人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.34,0:55:50.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It skirts the mountain and then...
Dialogue: 1,0:55:48.34,0:55:50.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这从山上...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.38,0:55:52.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...extends down towards the headwater here...
Dialogue: 1,0:55:50.38,0:55:52.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...一直到这里的水边...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.93,0:55:56.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and right across to the far bank of the Ohio River.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:52.93,0:55:56.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...跨越俄亥俄河
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.93,0:55:58.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's 100,000 acres.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:56.93,0:55:58.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一共十万英亩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.35,0:56:00.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's an imposing land grant, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,0:55:58.35,0:56:00.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好大一片土地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.90,0:56:03.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You will be a country unto yourself.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:00.90,0:56:03.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你可以自己成立一个小国家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.28,0:56:08.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,His Majesty is most generous.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:07.28,0:56:08.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,国王真的很大方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.74,0:56:15.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Though your service in this war more than warrants such a gift.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:11.74,0:56:15.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但是您在战争中的表现 也当之无愧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.58,0:56:21.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is how His Majesty rewards those...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:16.58,0:56:21.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的,国王对为他效命的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.54,0:56:23.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...who fight for him as gentlemen.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:21.54,0:56:23.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...就是这么大方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.88,0:56:27.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I dare to presume my own meager contributions will be rewarded one day.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:23.88,0:56:27.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我想我也有一天能得到奖赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.13,0:56:30.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You may presume too much.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:28.13,0:56:30.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你想的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.88,0:56:34.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,His Majesty, like history, judges us by the outcome of the war...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:30.88,0:56:34.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,国王看的不光是 战争的结果...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.64,0:56:36.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and the manner in which it was fought.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:34.64,0:56:36.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...也很注重作战的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.77,0:56:40.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We serve the Crown, and we must conduct ourselves accordingly.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:37.77,0:56:40.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们为英国皇室打仗 就要有个作战的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.81,0:56:43.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Surrendering troops will be given quarter.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:41.81,0:56:43.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们要善待投降的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.11,0:56:46.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These brutal tactics must stop!
Dialogue: 1,0:56:44.11,0:56:46.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这种惨无人道的事必须停止!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.07,0:56:49.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Is it not enough that I have never lost a battle?
Dialogue: 1,0:56:47.07,0:56:49.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我百战百胜还不够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.57,0:56:50.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You serve me...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:49.57,0:56:50.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你为我作战...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.95,0:56:55.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and the manner in which you serve me reflects upon me!
Dialogue: 1,0:56:50.95,0:56:55.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...你作战的方式 会影响别人对我的看法!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.49,0:56:59.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I would've thought that a gentleman from a family as esteemed as yours...
Dialogue: 1,0:56:56.49,0:56:59.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我以为像你这样的名门子弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.12,0:57:01.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...would understand that.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:00.12,0:57:01.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...应该了解这点才是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.67,0:57:06.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My late father squandered any esteem in which we were held...
Dialogue: 1,0:57:03.67,0:57:06.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我父亲把我的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.63,0:57:08.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...along with my inheritance.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:06.63,0:57:08.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,和自尊挥霍一空
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.97,0:57:14.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I advance myself only through victory.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:11.97,0:57:14.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,打胜仗是我力争上游的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.80,0:57:18.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You advance yourself only through my good graces.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:14.80,0:57:18.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你要靠我的战功才能得利
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.85,0:57:21.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These Colonials are our brethren.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:19.85,0:57:21.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,殖民地的人民是我们的弟兄
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.14,0:57:26.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And when this conflict is over, we will reestablish commerce with them.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:22.14,0:57:26.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战争结束之后我们会重修旧好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.44,0:57:29.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, colonel?
Dialogue: 1,0:57:27.44,0:57:29.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,懂吗,上校?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.65,0:57:32.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Perfectly, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:30.65,0:57:32.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,懂,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.53,0:58:18.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Reverend, with your permission, l'd like to make an announcement.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:15.53,0:58:18.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧师,如你允许 我想宣布一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.82,0:58:21.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Young man, this is a house of God.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:18.82,0:58:21.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,年轻人,这是上帝的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.33,0:58:25.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I understand that, reverend. I apologize.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:22.33,0:58:25.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我了解,牧师,请容我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.71,0:58:29.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The South Carolina Militia is being called up.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:26.71,0:58:29.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们来召集南卡民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.17,0:58:32.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm here to enlist every man willing.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:30.17,0:58:32.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,有志加入的人请来我这儿登记
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.46,0:58:34.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Son...
Dialogue: 1,0:58:33.46,0:58:34.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,年轻人...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.01,0:58:36.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...we are here to pray...
Dialogue: 1,0:58:35.01,0:58:36.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.05,0:58:39.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...for the souls of those men hanging outside.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:37.05,0:58:39.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为在外面被吊死的人祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.05,0:58:41.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, pray for them.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:40.05,0:58:41.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为他们祷告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.22,0:58:44.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But honor them by taking up arms with us.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:42.22,0:58:44.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但加入我们不要让他们白死
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.35,0:58:48.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And bring more suffering to this town?
Dialogue: 1,0:58:46.35,0:58:48.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,让人民吃更多苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.77,0:58:52.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If King George can hang those men, he can hang any one of us.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:48.77,0:58:52.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果英王乔治能吊死那些人 他就能吊死我们
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.44,0:58:55.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dan Scott...
Dialogue: 1,0:58:54.44,0:58:55.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,丹史考特...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.86,0:58:59.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...barely a week ago you railed for two hours about independence.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:55.86,0:58:59.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...一周前你大赞独立自主两小时
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.12,0:59:04.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hardwick, how many times have I heard you...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:02.12,0:59:04.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,哈伟先生,你在我家提及过
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.91,0:59:07.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...speak of freedom at my father's table?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:04.91,0:59:07.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,多少次自由?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.04,0:59:12.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Half the men in this church, including you, Father...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:09.04,0:59:12.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这里半数的人包括你 父亲...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.63,0:59:15.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and you, reverend...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:13.63,0:59:15.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...和你,牧师...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.88,0:59:18.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...are as ardent patriots as l.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:15.88,0:59:18.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...都和我一样爱国
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.47,0:59:27.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Will you now, when you are needed most, stop at only words?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:23.47,0:59:27.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们现在却只敢空谈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.48,0:59:30.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Is that the sort of men you are?
Dialogue: 1,0:59:28.48,0:59:30.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们是这种人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.91,0:59:42.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I ask only that you act upon the beliefs...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:39.91,0:59:42.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要求你们起而行...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.41,0:59:45.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...of which you have so strongly spoken...
Dialogue: 1,0:59:42.41,0:59:45.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...贯彻你们的理念...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.16,0:59:49.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and in which you so strongly believe.
Dialogue: 1,0:59:46.16,0:59:49.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...为你们的信仰奋斗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.43,1:00:02.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Who's with us?
Dialogue: 1,1:00:01.43,1:00:02.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谁要加入我们?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.70,1:01:05.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Howard.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:04.70,1:01:05.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,霍华先生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.95,1:01:07.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 1,1:01:06.95,1:01:07.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先生...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.45,1:01:10.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...may I have permission to write to Anne?
Dialogue: 1,1:01:08.45,1:01:10.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我可以写信给安吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.50,1:01:17.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-May I have permission to write Anne? -Yes.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:14.50,1:01:17.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我可以写信给安吗? -可以
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.67,1:01:20.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You have permission...
Dialogue: 1,1:01:18.67,1:01:20.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你可以...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.55,1:01:22.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...to write me.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:20.55,1:01:22.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...写信给我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.97,1:01:24.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, write her.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:22.97,1:01:24.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,写给她
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.35,1:01:27.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:26.35,1:01:27.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.72,1:01:30.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:29.72,1:01:30.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你,先生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.44,1:01:34.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Reverend?
Dialogue: 1,1:01:33.44,1:01:34.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧师?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.53,1:01:43.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A shepherd must tend his flock.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:41.53,1:01:43.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧羊人要保护他的羊群
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.99,1:01:48.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And, at times, fight off the wolves.
Dialogue: 1,1:01:44.99,1:01:48.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,有时要赶走野狼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.11,1:02:30.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the right place to recruit for a militia?
Dialogue: 1,1:02:27.11,1:02:30.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你确定这是合适的地方去找 民兵吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.79,1:02:39.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,God save King George!
Dialogue: 1,1:02:37.79,1:02:39.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,天佑吾王!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.10,1:03:01.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I think we came to the right place.
Dialogue: 1,1:02:59.10,1:03:01.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我想是来对地方了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.78,1:03:10.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Any bounty? -No scalp money this time, Rollins.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:07.78,1:03:10.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-有没有赏金? -这次恐怕没有赏金
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.78,1:03:15.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But you can keep or sell me the muskets and gear of any Redcoat you kill.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:10.78,1:03:15.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但你杀了红衫军就可以卖给我 他们的枪和装备
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.13,1:03:29.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They hanged my brother down in Acworth.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:27.13,1:03:29.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们在艾克华斯吊死我弟
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.51,1:03:33.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Every damned one of them Redcoats deserves to die.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:30.51,1:03:33.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那些红衫军都该死
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.35,1:03:34.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Sign up. -With all my ailments...
Dialogue: 1,1:03:33.35,1:03:34.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-那就加入我们 -我浑身残疾...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.14,1:03:38.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't make it through the first skirmish. No, sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:35.14,1:03:38.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我撑不到前哨战 我看还是算了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.31,1:03:41.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But you can have my Negro. He'll fight in my stead.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:38.31,1:03:41.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但是我的黑奴可以代我上阵
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.48,1:03:43.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Occam! Get over here.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:41.48,1:03:43.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,欧坎!过来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Ain't overly smart. He's strong as a bull.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他不聪明,但很强壮
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.32,1:03:49.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Can you write?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:48.32,1:03:49.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你会写字吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.32,1:03:52.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, no, sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:50.32,1:03:52.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.37,1:03:54.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Well, then, make your mark. -Why?
Dialogue: 1,1:03:52.37,1:03:54.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-那就画押吧 -为什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.54,1:03:56.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I just signed him over to you.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:54.54,1:03:56.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我把他让给你了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.45,1:03:58.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If you're willing, make your mark.
Dialogue: 1,1:03:56.45,1:03:58.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你愿意的话,我想要你画押
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.46,1:04:06.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That'll do.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:05.46,1:04:06.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.97,1:04:13.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll kill me some Redcoats.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:11.97,1:04:13.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要去杀红衫军
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.39,1:04:15.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I believe you would.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:14.39,1:04:15.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我相信你会
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.14,1:04:17.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 1,1:04:16.14,1:04:17.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你几岁?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.52,1:04:20.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not quite old enough. But his time will come.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:17.52,1:04:20.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还不够大 但时候会到的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.35,1:04:22.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,John Billings. I was hoping you'd turn up.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:20.35,1:04:22.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,约翰比林斯 我希望你会来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.02,1:04:25.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There's a story going around about 20 Redcoats...
Dialogue: 1,1:04:23.02,1:04:25.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,传说有20名红衫军...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.82,1:04:28.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...got killed by a ghost or some damn thing.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:25.82,1:04:28.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...被鬼杀了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.65,1:04:30.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Carried a Cherokee tomahawk.
Dialogue: 1,1:04:28.65,1:04:30.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这鬼带一个印第安斧头
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.36,1:04:35.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a little old to be believing in ghost stories?
Dialogue: 1,1:04:32.36,1:04:35.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你相信鬼故事不嫌老吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.64,1:05:43.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How many did you get?
Dialogue: 1,1:05:41.64,1:05:43.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你找到几个?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.81,1:05:44.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Twelve.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:43.81,1:05:44.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,12个
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.60,1:05:46.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:45.60,1:05:46.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.65,1:05:50.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These men, they're not the sort we need.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:47.65,1:05:50.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们要的不是这种人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.74,1:05:55.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're exactly the sort we need.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:53.74,1:05:55.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们要的正是这种人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.12,1:05:59.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They've fought this kind of war before.
Dialogue: 1,1:05:57.12,1:05:59.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们以前打过这种仗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.91,1:06:04.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What about me? Am I one of that sort?
Dialogue: 1,1:06:02.91,1:06:04.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那我呢?我也是之一吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:06.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hell, no.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:05.46,1:06:06.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,当然不
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.25,1:06:09.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your sort gives that sort a bad name.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:07.25,1:06:09.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你这种人把耻辱带给那种人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.01,1:06:18.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I want accuracy and precision.
Dialogue: 1,1:06:15.01,1:06:18.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要求快狠准
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.80,1:06:19.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Make ready!
Dialogue: 1,1:06:18.80,1:06:19.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.77,1:06:26.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 1,1:06:24.77,1:06:26.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄准!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.44,1:06:32.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,1:06:31.44,1:06:32.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.56,1:07:12.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Chattering
Dialogue: 1,1:07:10.56,1:07:12.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-悬赏：抓鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.23,1:07:13.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Anne:
Dialogue: 1,1:07:12.23,1:07:13.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,, -亲爱的安：
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.78,1:07:15.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Our force continues to grow.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:13.78,1:07:15.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的军力越来越强
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.07,1:07:20.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As long as we continue to fight, others will come to fight beside us.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:16.07,1:07:20.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,只要我们奋战不懈 其他人就会起而效尤
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.74,1:07:23.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I long to see you and speak to you.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:20.74,1:07:23.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我很想见你和跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.99,1:07:26.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm hopeful that our duties will bring me near you.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:23.99,1:07:26.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也希望我能因职务之便 靠近你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.79,1:07:31.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Until then, I am and will remain most affectionately yours.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:26.79,1:07:31.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在见面之前 我会时时想着你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.29,1:07:32.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel.
Dialogue: 1,1:07:31.29,1:07:32.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列上
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.70,1:08:00.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We surrender!
Dialogue: 1,1:07:58.70,1:08:00.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们投降!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.45,1:08:03.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No! God, stop!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:02.45,1:08:03.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不!天啊,不要!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.99,1:08:05.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,For the love of God, we...
Dialogue: 1,1:08:03.99,1:08:05.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看在老天的份上...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.70,1:08:08.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These men were about to surrender!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:06.70,1:08:08.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这些人就要投降了!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.37,1:08:11.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:10.37,1:08:11.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.92,1:08:13.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We will never know.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:11.92,1:08:13.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们永远也无从得知
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.46,1:08:14.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is murder!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:13.46,1:08:14.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是谋杀!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.09,1:08:18.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hell, reverend, they're Redcoats. They've earned it.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:15.09,1:08:18.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧师,他们是红衫军 他们罪该万死
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.01,1:08:23.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-We're better than that. -What do you know about war?
Dialogue: 1,1:08:21.01,1:08:23.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我们比他们好多了 -你对战争懂什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.64,1:08:25.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know the difference between fighting...
Dialogue: 1,1:08:23.64,1:08:25.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道为崇高目标而战...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.68,1:08:27.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go back to church!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:25.68,1:08:27.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,回你的教堂!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.60,1:08:28.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 1,1:08:27.60,1:08:28.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,安静!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.69,1:08:31.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:30.69,1:08:31.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他说的对
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.90,1:08:36.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Quarter will be given to British wounded and any who surrender.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.90,1:08:36.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们要收容那些受伤 及投降的英军
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.61,1:08:40.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They gave no quarter when they fired on a ship carrying my wife and daughters.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:36.61,1:08:40.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,当他们对我的妻儿坐的船 开火时也没想到要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.32,1:08:44.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I watched from 200 yards off as they were burned alive.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:41.32,1:08:44.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我在200码外 眼睁睁看着他们被烧死
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.66,1:08:48.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-All my sympathy, but my order stands. -Damn your sympathy.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:45.66,1:08:48.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我很同情你,但就这样 -去你的同情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.08,1:08:51.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Who are you to give such an order?
Dialogue: 1,1:08:49.08,1:08:51.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你凭什么下这种命令?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.17,1:08:55.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know what you did to my countrymen at Fort Wilderness.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:52.17,1:08:55.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你和你的手下在 维尔德尼斯堡是怎么对我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.92,1:09:01.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We're militia. This is not regular army.
Dialogue: 1,1:08:57.92,1:09:01.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们是民兵,不是正规军
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.26,1:09:04.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Every man here is free to come and go as he pleases.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:02.26,1:09:04.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这里的人可以自行决定去留
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.01,1:09:06.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But while you're here...
Dialogue: 1,1:09:05.01,1:09:06.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但你们留下来的话...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.47,1:09:09.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...you will obey my command or I will have you shot.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:06.47,1:09:09.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...就要听我的命令 否则军法处置
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.90,1:09:17.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Damn dogs! -Shoot the damn things!
Dialogue: 1,1:09:14.90,1:09:17.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-该死的狗辈! -杀了它们!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.19,1:09:18.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stay that pistol.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:17.19,1:09:18.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.94,1:09:20.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They won't let you near the wagon.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:18.94,1:09:20.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,它们不让任何人靠近车子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.33,1:09:28.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Rum, Madeira. -No wonder they were guarding it.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:26.33,1:09:28.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-是兰姆酒 -难怪它们看的这么紧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.99,1:09:30.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Officers' uniforms.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:28.99,1:09:30.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,军官的制服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.33,1:09:32.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What you think all this is worth?
Dialogue: 1,1:09:30.33,1:09:32.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们猜这值多少钱?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.71,1:09:37.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's the personal correspondence of Lord Cornwallis.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:33.71,1:09:37.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是康瓦理斯将军的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.38,1:09:40.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is his journal.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:39.38,1:09:40.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是他的日记
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.84,1:09:45.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I say we drink the wine, eat the dogs and use the papers for musket wadding.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:41.84,1:09:45.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们喝了他的酒,吃了他的狗 用这些纸来塞毛瑟枪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.22,1:09:47.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Eat the dogs?
Dialogue: 1,1:09:46.22,1:09:47.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,吃他的狗?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.72,1:09:50.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dog is a fine meal.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:48.72,1:09:50.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,狗肉很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.68,1:09:53.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Good heavens.
Dialogue: 1,1:09:51.68,1:09:53.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.24,1:10:08.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have some maps here for you.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:06.24,1:10:08.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我这里有地图
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.58,1:10:12.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Put them down over there. Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:09.58,1:10:12.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,放在那里,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.33,1:10:15.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Here. A proper musket for you.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:13.33,1:10:15.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,给你一把毛瑟枪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.92,1:10:20.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you, but I don't like the idea giving muskets to slaves.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:15.92,1:10:20.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你们怎么样 但我觉得不该让黑奴拿枪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.71,1:10:25.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your sense of freedom is as pale as your skin.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:22.71,1:10:25.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你对自由一点概念都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.81,1:10:33.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to them.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:31.81,1:10:33.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,别听他们的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.69,1:10:38.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If we win this war, a lot of things will change.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:35.69,1:10:38.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,打赢这场仗很多事都会变
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.11,1:10:40.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What will change?
Dialogue: 1,1:10:39.11,1:10:40.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,什么会变?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.11,1:10:46.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They call this the New World. It's not. It's the same as the old.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:42.11,1:10:46.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们说这里是新大陆 不是,这里和旧大陆一样
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.37,1:10:51.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But we'll have a chance to build a new world.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:49.37,1:10:51.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但我们有机会建立新世界
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:59.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A world where all men are created equal under God.
Dialogue: 1,1:10:55.04,1:10:59.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,新世界中人人平等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.29,1:11:01.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Equal.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:00.29,1:11:01.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,平等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.96,1:11:04.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:02.96,1:11:04.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,听起来很不错
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.76,1:11:08.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I've just been in the mind of a genius.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:05.76,1:11:08.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看了天才的杰作
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.89,1:11:15.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Cornwallis knows more about warfare than we could learn in a dozen lifetimes.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:10.89,1:11:15.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,康瓦理斯对战争的知识 丰富的令人咋舌
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.98,1:11:17.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's cheerful news.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:15.98,1:11:17.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那倒是令人振奋的好消息
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.77,1:11:22.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,His victories at Camden and Charles Town were perfect. Perfect.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:17.77,1:11:22.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他在坎登和查理士城的胜利 无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.07,1:11:24.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And he knows it, what's more.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:23.07,1:11:24.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,而且他心里明白
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.36,1:11:28.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's his weakness.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:27.36,1:11:28.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许这就是他的弱点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.24,1:11:30.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 1,1:11:29.24,1:11:30.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,长官?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.74,1:11:32.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Pride.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:31.74,1:11:32.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,骄傲
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.12,1:11:35.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Pride's a weakness.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:34.12,1:11:35.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,骄傲是弱点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.08,1:11:38.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Personally, I would prefer stupidity.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:36.08,1:11:38.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我还是希望他蠢一些
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.92,1:11:42.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Pride will do.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:40.92,1:11:42.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,骄傲就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.43,1:11:55.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Finished, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:53.43,1:11:55.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.77,1:11:57.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I've taken it in at the back...
Dialogue: 1,1:11:55.77,1:11:57.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我把背后改紧...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.98,1:12:00.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...added wider epaulets and looped gold braiding.
Dialogue: 1,1:11:57.98,1:12:00.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,加了肩章和金边
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.85,1:12:03.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-lt's a horse blanket. -I don't know, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:00.85,1:12:03.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-这简直是马用的毛毯 -这我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.19,1:12:06.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's really quite nice.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:04.19,1:12:06.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看起来很不错
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.86,1:12:09.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Very nice, my lord. -Very well. It's a nice horse blanket.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:06.86,1:12:09.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-非常不错 -这是一条很好的马毛毯
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.41,1:12:14.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel Tavington, why, after six weeks...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:11.41,1:12:14.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,塔维顿上校 为什么都等了六个星期...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.53,1:12:17.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...am I still attending a ball in South Carolina...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:14.53,1:12:17.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我还在南卡参加舞会...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.87,1:12:20.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...when I should be attending balls in North Carolina?
Dialogue: 1,1:12:17.87,1:12:20.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...而我现在应该早就在北卡了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.79,1:12:22.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,First, the theft of my baggage...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:20.79,1:12:22.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先是我的行李被偷...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.54,1:12:25.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...including my memoirs, on which I spent countless hours.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:22.54,1:12:25.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...包括我费尽心力写的日志
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.88,1:12:29.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Then half the bridges and ferries between here and Charles Town burned.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:25.88,1:12:29.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,接着从这儿到查理士城半数 以上的渡口及桥梁都被烧了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.88,1:12:32.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If you can't protect our supply lines against militia...
Dialogue: 1,1:12:29.88,1:12:32.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你无法对抗民兵 保护自己的补给线...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.93,1:12:36.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...how do you intend doing so against the Regulars or the French?
Dialogue: 1,1:12:32.93,1:12:36.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...你要怎么对抗正规军 和法军呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.60,1:12:39.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They won't fight like Regulars. We can't find them.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:36.60,1:12:39.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们不打正规战 我们找不到他们
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.39,1:12:41.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel, they're militia.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:39.39,1:12:41.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们是民兵
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.56,1:12:44.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're farmers with pitchforks!
Dialogue: 1,1:12:42.56,1:12:44.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们是拿着耙子的农夫!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.69,1:12:48.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're rather more than that, l'm afraid.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:45.69,1:12:48.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们不止是农夫
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.40,1:12:51.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Made so by their commander, this ghost.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:48.40,1:12:51.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们是鬼影指挥官调教的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.57,1:12:54.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, ghost, ghost, ghost.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:51.57,1:12:54.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,鬼,鬼,鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.03,1:12:57.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You created this ghost, colonel.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:55.03,1:12:57.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那个鬼是你塑造出来的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.45,1:13:00.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your brutality swelled his ranks.
Dialogue: 1,1:12:58.45,1:13:00.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他的阶级是你帮他挂的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.50,1:13:02.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Without them this ghost would've disappeared...
Dialogue: 1,1:13:00.50,1:13:02.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,要是没有他们就没有这个鬼...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.00,1:13:05.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and l'd be in North Carolina by now!
Dialogue: 1,1:13:03.00,1:13:05.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...而我现在已到北卡了!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.59,1:13:06.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,In my defense, my lord...
Dialogue: 1,1:13:05.59,1:13:06.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要为我辩护...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.13,1:13:08.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, enough, enough!
Dialogue: 1,1:13:07.13,1:13:08.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,够了...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.63,1:13:13.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A fine soldier you are, bested by a bedtime story.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:09.63,1:13:13.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,亏你是个好军人居然会怕鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.26,1:13:17.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the horse blanket.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:15.26,1:13:17.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把那个马毛毯给我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.43,1:13:23.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,O'Hara, our supply ship appears to have arrived.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:20.43,1:13:23.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,奥哈拉 我们的补给船似乎来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.10,1:13:25.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, my lord, it has.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:24.10,1:13:25.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.77,1:13:28.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Then why am I still wearing this rag?
Dialogue: 1,1:13:25.77,1:13:28.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那我为什么要穿这个地毯?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.44,1:13:31.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your replacement wardrobe is aboard ship, but...
Dialogue: 1,1:13:28.44,1:13:31.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,长官,您的礼服在船上 但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.53,1:13:35.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...Colonel Tavington thought it best to secure our arms and munitions first.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:31.53,1:13:35.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...塔维顿上校认为 要先搬军用品
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.91,1:13:37.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They are being unloaded.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:35.91,1:13:37.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,弟兄们现在正在搬
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.80,1:13:50.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You look good in that color.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:48.80,1:13:50.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你穿这个颜色很好看
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.30,1:13:53.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It stinks.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:52.30,1:13:53.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.55,1:13:57.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, it's had a dead man in it.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:55.55,1:13:57.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,原来是死人穿的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.76,1:13:59.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The beasts took your dogs too?
Dialogue: 1,1:13:57.76,1:13:59.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那些野蛮人连你的狗都不放过?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.93,1:14:01.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,1:13:59.93,1:14:01.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.18,1:14:05.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fine animals. A gift from His Majesty.
Dialogue: 1,1:14:02.18,1:14:05.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那两只好狗是国王送我的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.27,1:14:07.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dead now, for all I know.
Dialogue: 1,1:14:06.27,1:14:07.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,据我所知大概已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.27,1:14:10.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Is there no decency?
Dialogue: 1,1:14:08.27,1:14:10.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没有天理了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.74,1:14:23.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, fireworks. Lovely!
Dialogue: 1,1:14:19.74,1:14:23.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,太棒了!是烟火
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.49,1:14:56.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Howard.
Dialogue: 1,1:14:55.49,1:14:56.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,霍华先生
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.99,1:15:00.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I've come to call on Anne.
Dialogue: 1,1:14:57.99,1:15:00.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是来看安的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.91,1:15:09.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I've come to call on Anne!
Dialogue: 1,1:15:05.91,1:15:09.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是来看安的!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.21,1:15:11.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well, of course you call yourself a man.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:09.21,1:15:11.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你当然是个男人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.42,1:15:15.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father, stop it. You heard him.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:12.42,1:15:15.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲,别逗了 你听到他说的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.34,1:15:19.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 1,1:15:18.34,1:15:19.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.05,1:15:21.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...call on her.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:20.05,1:15:21.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...去看她吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.33,1:15:48.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm nearly finished.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:47.33,1:15:48.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我快好了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.42,1:15:52.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry, Father.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:50.42,1:15:52.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,别担心,父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.42,1:15:53.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:52.42,1:15:53.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.42,1:15:58.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Bundling bags are a wonderful tradition. I don't mind in the least.
Dialogue: 1,1:15:54.42,1:15:58.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得这布丁袋是很好的传统 我一点都不介意
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.09,1:16:01.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Be still.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:00.09,1:16:01.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.30,1:16:03.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tea?
Dialogue: 1,1:16:02.30,1:16:03.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,要茶吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.43,1:16:05.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:04.43,1:16:05.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.56,1:16:08.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:07.56,1:16:08.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.99,1:16:18.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Come, dear.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:16.99,1:16:18.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,来吧,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.79,1:16:31.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's very good.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:29.79,1:16:31.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.29,1:16:36.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased that you like it.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:34.29,1:16:36.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你喜欢我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.35,1:16:46.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Peter.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:45.35,1:16:46.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,彼德
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.27,1:16:50.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I sew better than my mother did.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:47.27,1:16:50.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,别担心 我的针上工夫比我妈好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.94,1:16:55.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 1,1:16:53.94,1:16:55.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,希望如此
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.65,1:17:03.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If you're just gonna stand there...
Dialogue: 1,1:17:01.65,1:17:03.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你只是站在那里...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.99,1:17:05.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...why don't you read it for us?
Dialogue: 1,1:17:03.99,1:17:05.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...为什么不念出来给我们听?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.95,1:17:07.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can't read.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:05.95,1:17:07.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不识字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.29,1:17:11.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:10.29,1:17:11.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.83,1:17:15.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,"Take notice.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:14.83,1:17:15.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,请注意
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.75,1:17:20.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,By order of General Washington and the Continental Congress...
Dialogue: 1,1:17:16.75,1:17:20.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,华盛顿将军及国会下令...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.51,1:17:23.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...all bound slaves who give minimum one year service...
Dialogue: 1,1:17:20.51,1:17:23.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...在独立军中...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.97,1:17:25.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...in the Continental Army...
Dialogue: 1,1:17:23.97,1:17:25.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,服役一年以上的奴隶...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.30,1:17:28.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will be granted freedom...
Dialogue: 1,1:17:26.30,1:17:28.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...将可重获自由...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.97,1:17:32.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and be paid a bounty of five shillings for each month of service."
Dialogue: 1,1:17:28.97,1:17:32.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...并可得到每个月 五先令的薪水
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.23,1:17:34.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,1:17:33.23,1:17:34.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.85,1:17:37.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,First they'll free them, then they'll pay them.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:34.85,1:17:37.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先是要放他们自由 接下来又要付他们钱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.40,1:17:40.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Only another six months.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:38.40,1:17:40.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,只要再六个月
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.32,1:17:45.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What will you do with freedom?
Dialogue: 1,1:17:43.32,1:17:45.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你自由后要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.50,1:17:58.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I made this for you.
Dialogue: 1,1:17:56.50,1:17:58.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是我帮你做的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.56,1:18:16.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Look after your mother.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:14.56,1:18:16.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好好照顾你妈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.86,1:18:23.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You know, Peter...
Dialogue: 1,1:18:21.86,1:18:23.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗,彼德...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.11,1:18:25.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I can't pay you for this.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:24.11,1:18:25.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我没有办法付你钱
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.86,1:18:30.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin, you pay me what you can, when you can.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:25.86,1:18:30.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你方便时再给
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.45,1:18:31.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm obliged.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:30.45,1:18:31.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.25,1:18:36.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel sure reminds me a lot of you.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:33.25,1:18:36.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列真的很像你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.75,1:18:40.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No, no, he's more like his mother.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:37.75,1:18:40.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不,他比较像他妈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.88,1:18:42.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Corporal!
Dialogue: 1,1:18:41.88,1:18:42.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,下士!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.55,1:18:46.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Take your time. Dogs.
Dialogue: 1,1:18:44.55,1:18:46.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你慢慢来,狗儿们
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.74,1:19:04.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:03.74,1:19:04.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.12,1:19:52.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This road is closed.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:51.12,1:19:52.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,道路封闭了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.45,1:19:55.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,These wagons now belong to the Continental Army.
Dialogue: 1,1:19:53.45,1:19:55.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这些车辆现在正式成为 独立军的财产
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.16,1:19:58.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Ready arms!
Dialogue: 1,1:19:56.16,1:19:58.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.47,1:20:12.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,By twos!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:11.47,1:20:12.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,排成两列
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.94,1:20:25.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There's no need for your men to die. Leave the wagons and go.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:21.94,1:20:25.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你和你的手下不必死 留下车子就走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.03,1:20:27.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is the king's highway.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:26.03,1:20:27.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是国王的公路
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.15,1:20:30.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And I advise you and your men to make way.
Dialogue: 1,1:20:28.15,1:20:30.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我劝你和你的手下让开
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.75,1:20:38.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:37.75,1:20:38.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,进攻!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.87,1:20:41.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:39.87,1:20:41.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.33,1:20:43.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:42.33,1:20:43.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.72,1:20:52.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Save yourselves!
Dialogue: 1,1:20:50.72,1:20:52.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,保留实力!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.29,1:21:21.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:20.29,1:21:21.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.89,1:21:42.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Ambush! Ambush!
Dialogue: 1,1:21:39.89,1:21:42.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,有埋伏...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.80,1:22:17.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have the count.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:15.80,1:22:17.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我统计了一下
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.93,1:22:20.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,22 are dead.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:18.93,1:22:20.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,死了二十二个人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.47,1:22:23.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,18 wounded and 20 are missing.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:21.47,1:22:23.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,十八个人受伤 二十人失踪
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.10,1:22:25.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm through.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:24.10,1:22:25.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.44,1:22:33.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He won't be the last to leave.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:31.44,1:22:33.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他不是最后一个要走的人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.82,1:22:36.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Trust me. Soon my countrymen will arrive.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:33.82,1:22:36.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,相信我,我的同胞很快就会到
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.28,1:22:38.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-The French army is... -To hell with you.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:36.28,1:22:38.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-法国军队... -你下地狱
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.45,1:22:39.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And to hell with the French army.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:38.45,1:22:39.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,法国军队下地狱
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.20,1:22:41.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We don't need them.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:40.20,1:22:41.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们不需要他们
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.62,1:22:44.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We got Benjamin Martin. We know what he done to the French.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:41.62,1:22:44.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们有班杰明马汀,我们知道 他是怎么对付法国人的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.35,1:23:00.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,1:22:59.35,1:23:00.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.22,1:23:05.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Men always buy you drinks because of what happened at Fort Wilderness.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:01.22,1:23:05.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你在维尔德尼斯堡的英勇事迹 人人佩服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.02,1:23:10.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Strangers know more about you than I do.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:08.02,1:23:10.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,陌生人都比我了解你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.78,1:23:14.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:12.78,1:23:14.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我当时的情况
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.53,1:23:20.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your mother asked me that question around about the time you were born.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:15.53,1:23:20.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你出生时 你母亲也问过我这个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.99,1:23:25.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I was drunk and foolish enough to answer it.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:22.99,1:23:25.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我当时烂醉如泥才会回答
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.34,1:23:35.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The French and the Cherokee had raided along the Blue Ridge.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:32.34,1:23:35.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,法国人和印地安人 突击蓝桥
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.55,1:23:39.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The English settlers had sought refuge at Fort Charles.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:36.55,1:23:39.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,英国殖民到查尔斯堡寻求庇护
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.05,1:23:43.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,By the time we got there, the fort was abandoned.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:40.05,1:23:43.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们抵达时那里已经没人了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.60,1:23:46.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'd left about a week before.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:44.60,1:23:46.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们一周前就离开了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.19,1:23:50.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But what we found was....
Dialogue: 1,1:23:48.19,1:23:50.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但是我们发现...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.52,1:23:54.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:53.52,1:23:54.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,继续说
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.86,1:24:01.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'd killed all the settlers, the men.
Dialogue: 1,1:23:57.86,1:24:01.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们杀光所有的男的殖民
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.41,1:24:05.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,With the women and...
Dialogue: 1,1:24:03.41,1:24:05.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,女人和...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.41,1:24:07.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...some of the children, they had....
Dialogue: 1,1:24:05.41,1:24:07.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...某些孩童被他们...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.75,1:24:13.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We buried them all, what was left of them.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:10.75,1:24:13.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们把他们的遗骸全埋了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.38,1:24:19.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We caught up with them at Fort Wilderness.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:16.38,1:24:19.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们在维尔德尼斯堡追上他们
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.14,1:24:23.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We took our time.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:22.14,1:24:23.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们好整以暇
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.06,1:24:29.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We cut them apart slowly.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:26.06,1:24:29.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把他们五马分尸
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.77,1:24:31.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:29.77,1:24:31.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,千刀万剐
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.78,1:24:38.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can see their faces.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:36.78,1:24:38.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们的脸庞历历在目
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.07,1:24:44.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can still hear their screams.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:42.07,1:24:44.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,耳边彷彿回荡着他们的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.41,1:24:49.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All but two. We let them live.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:46.41,1:24:49.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们只留了两个活口
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.12,1:24:53.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We sent the heads on a pallet...
Dialogue: 1,1:24:51.12,1:24:53.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们让那两个人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.42,1:24:56.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...with the two that lived back to Fort Ambercon.
Dialogue: 1,1:24:53.42,1:24:56.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,带着那些人的项上人头回去
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.84,1:25:00.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The eyes, tongues, fingers...
Dialogue: 1,1:24:56.84,1:25:00.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,眼睛,舌头,手指...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.34,1:25:02.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...we put in baskets.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:00.34,1:25:02.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我们则装在篮子里
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.64,1:25:05.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sent them down the Asheulot to the Cherokee.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:02.64,1:25:05.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,送到印地安人那儿去
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.60,1:25:11.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Soon after, the Cherokee broke their treaty with the French.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:07.60,1:25:11.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不久后,印地安人 便不再与法国人合作
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.94,1:25:15.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's how we justified it.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:13.94,1:25:15.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们就是这样平衡的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.99,1:25:26.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We were...
Dialogue: 1,1:25:24.99,1:25:26.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们是...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.99,1:25:29.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...heroes.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:27.99,1:25:29.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.79,1:25:33.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And men bought you drinks.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:31.79,1:25:33.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那些人请你喝酒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.67,1:25:42.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not a day goes by where I don't ask God's forgiveness for what I did.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:38.67,1:25:42.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我每天都在祈求上帝宽恕我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.85,1:25:54.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thomas was my brother, as well as your son.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:50.85,1:25:54.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,汤玛斯是我的弟弟 也是你的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.19,1:25:59.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You may not believe this, but I want satisfaction as much as you do.
Dialogue: 1,1:25:55.19,1:25:59.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你也许不信 但我和你一样想要报仇
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.15,1:26:03.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But not at the expense of our cause.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:01.15,1:26:03.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但在不影响原则下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.41,1:26:07.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There will be a time for revenge.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:04.41,1:26:07.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,仇终究是要报的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.99,1:26:10.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But until then, stay the course.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:07.99,1:26:10.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但在那之前我会为自由奋斗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.58,1:26:15.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your mother said that when l'd get drunk or lose my temper.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:12.58,1:26:15.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我喝醉或发脾气时 你妈会说这句话
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.00,1:26:18.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,She'd say it to me when I picked on Thomas.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:16.00,1:26:18.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我挑汤玛斯毛病时她会这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.51,1:26:25.84,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I miss him.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:24.51,1:26:25.84,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我好想他
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.40,1:26:45.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The British got 18 of our men at Fort Carolina.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:42.40,1:26:45.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们有十八名弟兄 在卡罗莱纳州堡被俘
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.16,1:26:48.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They'll be hung one at a time until they give up the rest of us.
Dialogue: 1,1:26:46.16,1:26:48.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,除非他们说出我们的下落 否则都会被吊死
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.92,1:27:06.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Reverend...
Dialogue: 1,1:27:04.92,1:27:06.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧师...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.43,1:27:08.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...can you write a letter for me?
Dialogue: 1,1:27:06.43,1:27:08.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...能帮我写封信吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.89,1:27:11.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-To my wife and boy. -Yes, of course I will.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:08.89,1:27:11.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-写给我太太和儿子 -没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.72,1:27:14.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But first let us pray.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:11.72,1:27:14.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不过我们先来祷告
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.57,1:27:30.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 1,1:27:29.57,1:27:30.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大人...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.78,1:27:32.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...there is a rider at the gates.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:30.78,1:27:32.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...大门外有一名骑士
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.83,1:27:35.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A civilian carrying a white flag.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:32.83,1:27:35.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一名举白旗的平民
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.00,1:27:37.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I am occupied.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:36.00,1:27:37.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.08,1:27:40.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He has a pair of dogs with him.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:38.08,1:27:40.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他带了两只狗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.09,1:27:43.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Great Danes.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:41.09,1:27:43.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是大丹狗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.46,1:27:45.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And dear Lord...
Dialogue: 1,1:27:44.46,1:27:45.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,主啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.67,1:27:48.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...protect us in this, our hour of need.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:45.67,1:27:48.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...请在这个危急的时刻 保佑我们
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.26,1:27:51.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This we ask in the name of the Father, the Son....
Dialogue: 1,1:27:48.26,1:27:51.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们以圣父,圣子...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.10,1:27:53.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:52.10,1:27:53.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,和圣灵之名求您
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.94,1:28:00.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 1,1:27:58.94,1:28:00.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在这里等
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.48,1:28:02.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,General Lord Cornwallis will be with you shortly.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:00.48,1:28:02.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,康瓦理斯将军马上来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.32,1:28:49.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Jupiter, Mars. Come, boys.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:46.32,1:28:48.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,木星,土星,来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.11,1:28:53.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:52.11,1:28:53.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.58,1:29:00.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My good boys. My brave boys. You seem to be well-fed.
Dialogue: 1,1:28:56.58,1:29:00.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的乖狗狗 你们似乎没有吃苦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.37,1:29:04.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I thank you for that.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:02.37,1:29:04.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.21,1:29:06.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't know your name.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:04.21,1:29:06.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我还不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.00,1:29:11.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm a colonel in the Continental Army. My rank should be sufficient for now.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:07.00,1:29:11.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我是独立军的上校 你只要知道这个就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.09,1:29:13.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:12.09,1:29:13.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.39,1:29:15.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Please be seated.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:14.39,1:29:15.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.85,1:29:16.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:15.85,1:29:16.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.72,1:29:22.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Would you, as the initiating officer, care to begin?
Dialogue: 1,1:29:18.72,1:29:22.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,请你开始说明来意吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.02,1:29:25.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I will, unless you'd like to claim aggrieved status.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:23.02,1:29:25.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会的,除非你要先申报你的损失
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.15,1:29:28.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would like to claim aggrieved status.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:26.15,1:29:28.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的,我要先这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.03,1:29:30.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well, sir. Proceed.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:29.03,1:29:30.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那么,请继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.07,1:29:35.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You have in your possession belongings of mine including clothing...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:31.07,1:29:35.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你手上有我的私人物品 包括衣服...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.70,1:29:39.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...furniture, personal effects of a non-military nature...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:35.70,1:29:39.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...傢俱及私人日志...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.91,1:29:41.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...which l'd like returned to me.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:39.91,1:29:41.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我希望你能还我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.12,1:29:44.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I will do so as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:42.12,1:29:44.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会尽快办到的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.42,1:29:47.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:46.42,1:29:47.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.88,1:29:51.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Now we come to the matter of the specific targeting...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:47.88,1:29:51.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们来谈谈 你们在战场上...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.26,1:29:53.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...of officers during engagements.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:51.26,1:29:53.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...针对我们军官开枪的事
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.59,1:29:56.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You must know that in civilized warfare, officers in the field...
Dialogue: 1,1:29:53.59,1:29:56.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你应该知道在文明战争中 战场上的军官...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.01,1:30:01.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...must not be accorded inappropriate levels of hostile attention.
Dialogue: 1,1:29:57.01,1:30:01.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...不该表现出不合时宜的敌意
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.39,1:30:05.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To your mind, what are appropriate levels of hostile attention?
Dialogue: 1,1:30:02.39,1:30:05.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你认为怎样才叫做 不合时宜的敌意?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.19,1:30:08.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Imagine the chaos that would follow...
Dialogue: 1,1:30:06.19,1:30:08.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,想想看要是群龙无首...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.73,1:30:11.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...from leaderless armies having at each other.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:08.73,1:30:11.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...两军相争时会如何混乱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.32,1:30:15.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There must be gentlemen in command to lead...
Dialogue: 1,1:30:12.32,1:30:15.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一定要有指挥官...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.78,1:30:19.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and, where necessary, restrain their men.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:15.78,1:30:19.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...才能够在必要时控制军队
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.12,1:30:24.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Restrain them from, say, targeting civilians. Women, children and such.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:20.12,1:30:24.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,例如不让他们欺凌老弱妇孺
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.59,1:30:28.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's a separate issue.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:27.59,1:30:28.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那又是另一回事了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.96,1:30:30.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No. I consider them linked.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:28.96,1:30:30.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不,我认为是同一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.63,1:30:34.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And as long as your soldiers attack civilians...
Dialogue: 1,1:30:31.63,1:30:34.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,只要你的手下攻击平民百姓...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.55,1:30:37.64,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I will order the shooting of officers at every engagement.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:34.55,1:30:37.64,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我就会命令我的手下开战时 屠杀你的军官
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.31,1:30:42.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And my men are excellent marksmen.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:40.31,1:30:42.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的手下都是神枪手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.90,1:30:47.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:46.90,1:30:47.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.65,1:30:51.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Now, let us move on to... -Prisoner exchange.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:48.65,1:30:51.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-让我们继续讨论... -战俘交换事宜
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.65,1:30:53.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 1,1:30:52.65,1:30:53.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.49,1:30:57.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You have 18 of my men. I want them back.
Dialogue: 1,1:30:54.49,1:30:57.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我这边的确有十八名犯人 我要你放了他们
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.62,1:31:09.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I do have 18 criminals under sentence of death...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:04.62,1:31:09.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我这边的确有十八名死囚
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.54,1:31:12.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but I hold no prisoners of war.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:09.54,1:31:12.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...但我绝对不会扣留战犯
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.59,1:31:15.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If that's your position, 18 of your officers will have to die.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:12.59,1:31:15.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果那是你的立场,你就要 为你十八名军官的死负责
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.80,1:31:17.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Nineteen, if you hang me with my men.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:15.80,1:31:17.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,十九名,如果你把我一起吊死
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.14,1:31:19.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My officers?
Dialogue: 1,1:31:18.14,1:31:19.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的军官?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.35,1:31:20.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:19.35,1:31:20.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.98,1:31:30.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Top of the ridge, to your left. Below the tree line.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:27.98,1:31:30.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在你左方的山顶的树下
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.04,1:31:45.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Their names and ranks?
Dialogue: 1,1:31:44.04,1:31:45.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们的名字和官阶?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.58,1:31:49.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They refused to give names. There are 9 lieutenants, 5 captains, 3 majors...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:45.58,1:31:49.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们不透露姓名,有九名少尉 五名上尉,三名少校...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.75,1:31:51.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and one fat colonel who called me...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:49.75,1:31:51.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...和一个说我厚颜无耻的...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.50,1:31:55.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...a cheeky fellow.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:53.50,1:31:55.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...肥上尉
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.67,1:31:58.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is not the conduct of a gentleman.
Dialogue: 1,1:31:55.67,1:31:58.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这不是绅士该有的作为
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.63,1:32:01.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If the conduct of your officers is the measure of a gentleman...
Dialogue: 1,1:31:58.63,1:32:01.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你军官的作为 叫绅士作风的话...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.89,1:32:03.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:01.89,1:32:03.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...那我觉得你这是天大的恭维
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.97,1:32:07.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Get my men.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:05.97,1:32:07.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,去带我的手下来
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.11,1:32:13.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Arrange the exchange. -My lord.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:11.11,1:32:13.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-安排交换事宜 -大人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.11,1:32:15.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:14.11,1:32:15.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.77,1:32:48.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Release the prisoners!
Dialogue: 1,1:32:46.77,1:32:48.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,释放囚犯!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.40,1:32:55.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-What is this? -Prisoner exchange.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:53.40,1:32:55.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-将军,这是做什么? -交换战俘
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.77,1:32:57.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He has 18 of our officers.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:55.77,1:32:57.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他俘掳了我们十八名军官
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.53,1:32:59.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Who is he? I recognize him.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:57.53,1:32:59.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他是谁?我看过他
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.90,1:33:01.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's the commander of the militia.
Dialogue: 1,1:32:59.90,1:33:01.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他是民兵的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.99,1:33:03.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your ghost.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:02.99,1:33:03.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,就是你说的鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.20,1:33:05.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stay that sword, colonel!
Dialogue: 1,1:33:04.20,1:33:05.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要动,上校!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.20,1:33:08.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He rode in under a white flag for formal parley.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:06.20,1:33:08.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他举着白旗前来谈判 没有敌意,    是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.79,1:33:10.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is madness.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:08.79,1:33:10.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.75,1:33:12.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If you harm him, you condemn our officers.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:10.75,1:33:12.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果你伤害他的话 会害死我们的军官
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.50,1:33:18.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,With respect, sir, he's killed as many officers in the last two months.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:14.50,1:33:18.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,请恕我说一句 他过去已经杀了不少军官
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.01,1:33:23.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He has shown no aggression here. Hence he cannot be touched.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:19.01,1:33:23.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他没有敌意 所以我们不能伤害他
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.80,1:33:25.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Has he not?
Dialogue: 1,1:33:23.80,1:33:25.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.97,1:33:29.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 1,1:33:28.97,1:33:29.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.64,1:33:33.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,So you're the ghost, are you? I remember you!
Dialogue: 1,1:33:30.64,1:33:33.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,原来你就是那个鬼,我记得你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.85,1:33:35.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,On that farm! That stupid little boy!
Dialogue: 1,1:33:33.85,1:33:35.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在农场上!那个笨小孩
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.95,1:33:44.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Did he die?
Dialogue: 1,1:33:42.95,1:33:44.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.45,1:33:49.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 1,1:33:48.45,1:33:49.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.00,1:33:52.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...it's an ugly business, doing one's duty.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:50.00,1:33:52.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...有时克尽职责实在很不好受
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.83,1:33:54.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But just occasionally...
Dialogue: 1,1:33:52.83,1:33:54.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但有时候...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.63,1:33:57.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...it's a real pleasure.
Dialogue: 1,1:33:55.63,1:33:57.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...是赏心乐事
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.38,1:34:04.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Before this war is over, l'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 1,1:34:01.38,1:34:04.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在这场战争结束之前 我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.81,1:34:09.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Why wait?
Dialogue: 1,1:34:07.81,1:34:09.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为什么要等?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.69,1:34:19.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Soon.
Dialogue: 1,1:34:18.69,1:34:19.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很快的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.85,1:34:54.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Move out!
Dialogue: 1,1:34:52.85,1:34:54.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,出发!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.86,1:35:02.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But I still think it's imperative to push north.
Dialogue: 1,1:34:58.86,1:35:02.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我还是觉得北进太鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.36,1:35:07.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,One of our captured officers, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:05.36,1:35:07.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们被俘的军官之一
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.58,1:35:15.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My reputation suffers because of your incompetence!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:12.58,1:35:15.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们的无能害我脸上无光!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.12,1:35:19.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That man insults me!
Dialogue: 1,1:35:16.12,1:35:19.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那傢伙羞辱我!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.88,1:35:23.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Quite impressive for a farmer with a pitchfork, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 1,1:35:19.88,1:35:23.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这乡巴佬还真不简单
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.80,1:35:33.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I want you to find that man.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:30.80,1:35:33.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要你去找他
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.22,1:35:36.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I want you to capture him.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:34.22,1:35:36.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要你把他捉来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The man has the loyalty of the people.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,人民对他很忠心
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.40,1:35:42.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They protect him. Protect his family.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:40.40,1:35:42.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们保护他和他的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.94,1:35:44.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Protect the families of his men.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:42.94,1:35:44.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,保护他手下的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.99,1:35:47.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I can capture him for you.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:45.99,1:35:47.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你捉到他
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.57,1:35:53.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But to do so requires the use of tactics that are somewhat....
Dialogue: 1,1:35:49.57,1:35:53.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但是这就要用到一些 比较不光明的手段...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.70,1:35:56.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What was the word your lordship used?
Dialogue: 1,1:35:54.70,1:35:56.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大人之前是怎么说的?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.79,1:36:00.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,"Brutal," I think.
Dialogue: 1,1:35:58.79,1:36:00.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好像说“残忍”
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.13,1:36:10.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:09.13,1:36:10.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.27,1:36:21.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I am prepared to do what is necessary.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:19.27,1:36:21.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我准备好去做该做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.19,1:36:26.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I alone will assume the full mantle of responsibility for my actions...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:22.19,1:36:26.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我愿意为我的行为负全责...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.82,1:36:28.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...free of the chain of command...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:26.82,1:36:28.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我不受上级指挥...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.15,1:36:31.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...rendering you blameless.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:29.15,1:36:31.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...不管我做什么你都不能怪我
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.07,1:36:33.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:32.07,1:36:33.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.78,1:36:35.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...if I do this...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:33.78,1:36:35.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我这么做...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.66,1:36:39.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...you and I both know that I can never return to England with honor.
Dialogue: 1,1:36:35.66,1:36:39.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我们两个都知道 我永远无法载誉归国
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.88,1:36:46.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What, I wonder, is to become of me?
Dialogue: 1,1:36:42.88,1:36:46.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我将会有何下场?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.22,1:36:57.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,When this war is over here in the Colonies...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:54.22,1:36:57.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,当这里的战争结束之后...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.64,1:36:59.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...the new aristocracy...
Dialogue: 1,1:36:57.64,1:36:59.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...新兴贵族...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.52,1:37:03.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will be landowners.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:01.52,1:37:03.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...将会是地主
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.65,1:37:13.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tell me about Ohio.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:10.65,1:37:13.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我俄亥俄州的事
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.87,1:37:20.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Make way.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:18.87,1:37:20.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.21,1:37:22.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As you were.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:21.21,1:37:22.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,稍息
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.59,1:37:29.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Wilkins. A plantation seven miles from Wakefield, on the Santee...
Dialogue: 1,1:37:25.59,1:37:29.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,威尔金,离维克菲尔七英哩处...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.88,1:37:32.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...east of Black Swamp. Who lived there?
Dialogue: 1,1:37:29.88,1:37:32.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...山提河东岸的黑沼泽 是什么人住的?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.22,1:37:35.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin Martin.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:34.22,1:37:35.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明马汀
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.85,1:37:36.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He's the ghost.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:35.85,1:37:36.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他就是我们说的鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.47,1:37:39.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What do you know about him?
Dialogue: 1,1:37:38.47,1:37:39.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你对他知道多少?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.89,1:37:43.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hell, everything. I could tell you the size of his boot.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:39.89,1:37:43.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,无所不知 我连他几号鞋都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.44,1:37:48.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Does he have family? Where would he hide his children?
Dialogue: 1,1:37:44.44,1:37:48.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他有家人吗? 他把孩子藏在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.16,1:37:59.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,His wife's sister has a plantation.
Dialogue: 1,1:37:57.16,1:37:59.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他的小姨子有一个农庄
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.29,1:38:01.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's not far.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:00.29,1:38:01.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不远
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.61,1:38:38.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Aunt Charlotte! Wake up, someone's coming!
Dialogue: 1,1:38:35.61,1:38:38.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,夏绿蒂阿姨醒醒,有人来了!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.29,1:38:46.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Get the boys.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:44.29,1:38:46.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,去叫孩子们
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.38,1:38:51.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Margaret, come quickly.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:48.38,1:38:51.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,玛格莉特,快来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.25,1:38:54.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Let's go. -Boys, come.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:51.25,1:38:54.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我们走 -孩子们,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.63,1:38:55.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 1,1:38:54.63,1:38:55.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,快!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.31,1:39:02.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stay close.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:00.31,1:39:02.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,跟着我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.81,1:39:09.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:07.81,1:39:09.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,走这边 从窗台下出去
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.71,1:39:26.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:25.71,1:39:26.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,跟着我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.34,1:39:32.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We'll go downstairs to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 1,1:39:30.34,1:39:32.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们下楼到厨房
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.05,1:39:41.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Margaret, quick! Get down there! Fast!
Dialogue: 1,1:39:39.05,1:39:41.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,玛格莉特,快! 从这下面!快!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.19,1:39:55.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Samuel, get down there fast!
Dialogue: 1,1:39:53.19,1:39:55.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,山缪,快下来!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.58,1:40:54.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Beneath the sill. There.
Dialogue: 1,1:40:52.58,1:40:54.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在下面,那里
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.17,1:40:58.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There's no one in the house.
Dialogue: 1,1:40:57.17,1:40:58.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,房子里没有人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.92,1:41:00.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They can't be far.
Dialogue: 1,1:40:58.92,1:41:00.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们一定没走远
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.76,1:41:03.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Search the outbuildings and the woods, quickly.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:00.76,1:41:03.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,去树林里找找
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.92,1:41:42.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire the house.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:40.92,1:41:42.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备放火烧房子
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.55,1:41:44.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 1,1:41:43.55,1:41:44.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.66,1:42:06.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This one's head of the house slaves.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:04.66,1:42:06.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是他们家里的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.83,1:42:13.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where are they hiding?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:11.83,1:42:13.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们躲在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.25,1:42:19.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Keep looking! They're here somewhere!
Dialogue: 1,1:42:17.25,1:42:19.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,继续找,他们一定在附近!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.51,1:42:27.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Gabriel. -Where's Father?
Dialogue: 1,1:42:25.51,1:42:27.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-佳百列 -父亲呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.47,1:42:29.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Torch the house!
Dialogue: 1,1:42:27.47,1:42:29.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,放火烧房子!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.87,1:42:47.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To horse!
Dialogue: 1,1:42:46.87,1:42:47.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上马!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.21,1:42:56.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's all right.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:55.21,1:42:56.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.13,1:42:59.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Susan, come here.
Dialogue: 1,1:42:57.13,1:42:59.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,苏珊,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.22,1:43:09.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Charlotte!
Dialogue: 1,1:43:08.22,1:43:09.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,夏绿蒂!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.24,1:43:28.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They won't stop looking for us.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:25.24,1:43:28.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们不会放弃找我们的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.41,1:43:32.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe where we're taking you.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:30.41,1:43:32.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们会带你们去安全的地方
Dialogue: 1,1:43:33.37,1:43:36.08,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲说在那里藏身最适合了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.37,1:43:36.08,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father said it was a perfect place to hide.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:38.58,1:43:40.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.58,1:43:40.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 1,1:43:45.42,1:43:47.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道,我是他的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.42,1:43:47.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'm his son.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:47.38,1:43:49.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.38,1:43:49.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where is Father?
Dialogue: 1,1:43:50.76,1:43:52.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,几个月前开始说话
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.76,1:43:52.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Speaking for months now.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:52.60,1:43:54.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,几个月前开始说话
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.60,1:43:54.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Speaking for months.
Dialogue: 1,1:43:54.39,1:43:56.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.39,1:43:56.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Why did he go?
Dialogue: 1,1:43:58.40,1:44:02.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他不要那些人找到你们 所以他引他们离开
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.40,1:44:02.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He didn't want those mean men to find you, so he led them away.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:02.48,1:44:04.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他会尽快回来看你们
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.48,1:44:04.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He'll come see you as soon as he can.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:05.28,1:44:07.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不管,我恨他
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.28,1:44:07.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I don't care. I hate him.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:09.49,1:44:11.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,苏珊,你不恨他
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.49,1:44:11.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Susan, you don't hate him.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:11.45,1:44:14.95,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我恨他,我希望他永远不回来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.45,1:44:14.95,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I hate him, and I hope he never comes back.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:48.78,1:44:50.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是孩子们
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.78,1:44:50.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's the children.
Dialogue: 1,1:44:51.70,1:44:52.74,对白中文,,0,0,0,,艾比佳!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.70,1:44:52.74,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Abigale!
Dialogue: 1,1:44:54.58,1:44:56.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你还活着!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.58,1:44:56.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 1,1:45:05.30,1:45:09.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她说话了,苏珊跟你说话了?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.30,1:45:09.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,She spoke. Susan talked to you?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:09.34,1:45:10.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,整句
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.34,1:45:10.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,In full sentences.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:11.18,1:45:13.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好像她一直都可以说话
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.18,1:45:13.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,As if she'd been speaking all along.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:16.18,1:45:18.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,可恶,我居然不在场
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.18,1:45:18.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Damn, I wasn't there for it.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:19.35,1:45:20.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她说什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.35,1:45:20.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:23.06,1:45:24.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她说...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.06,1:45:24.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,She said...
Dialogue: 1,1:45:26.36,1:45:29.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...她很爱你也很想你...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.36,1:45:29.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...that she loves you and misses you...
Dialogue: 1,1:45:29.86,1:45:32.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她也了解你为什么不能来陪她
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.86,1:45:32.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but understands why you can't be with her.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:35.58,1:45:37.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,天啊,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.58,1:45:37.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My Lord, she said that.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:38.04,1:45:39.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.04,1:45:39.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:43.54,1:45:46.42,对白中文,,0,0,0,,塔维顿手上有我们的名单 他在烧我们的房子...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.54,1:45:46.42,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tavington has a list of our men. He's burning our homes...
Dialogue: 1,1:45:46.63,1:45:48.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...若有不从,格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.63,1:45:48.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...killing whomever resists.
Dialogue: 1,1:45:49.17,1:45:50.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.17,1:45:50.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,1:45:50.38,1:45:52.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他烧了山提河岸的七栋房子
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.38,1:45:52.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Seven homes along the Santee so far.
Dialogue: 1,1:46:51.28,1:46:53.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在不是报仇的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.28,1:46:53.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,John, this is not a time for vengeance.
Dialogue: 1,1:46:54.45,1:46:57.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是哀悼的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.45,1:46:57.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This is a time for mourning.
Dialogue: 1,1:47:31.48,1:47:33.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,去照顾你们的家人
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.48,1:47:33.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Attend to your families.
Dialogue: 1,1:47:35.61,1:47:37.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,所有的人都放一周假
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.61,1:47:37.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,One week furlough for all men.
Dialogue: 1,1:47:38.74,1:47:43.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果收假时不回来的人 不会当你是懦夫临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.74,1:47:43.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Any man who does not return will not be thought a coward or uncommitted.
Dialogue: 1,1:47:59.14,1:48:00.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.14,1:48:00.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 1,1:48:02.01,1:48:03.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.01,1:48:03.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 1,1:48:09.85,1:48:11.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,天啊,他们长得好大 你给他们吃什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.85,1:48:11.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're huge. What have you been feeding them?
Dialogue: 1,1:48:11.98,1:48:15.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们有爸爸的优良血统
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.98,1:48:15.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're from good stock on their father's side.
Dialogue: 1,1:48:23.79,1:48:25.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,苏珊?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.79,1:48:25.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Susan?
Dialogue: 1,1:49:05.24,1:49:08.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我看到了,在那里 快看,父亲!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:08.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I see it. There it is. Look. Look, father.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:10.75,1:49:12.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我抓到了...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.75,1:49:12.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 1,1:49:13.08,1:49:14.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你抓到了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.08,1:49:14.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:14.88,1:49:16.21,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我抓到了!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.88,1:49:16.21,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 1,1:49:16.42,1:49:17.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-小心 -我抓到了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.42,1:49:17.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Careful. -I caught it.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:17.76,1:49:20.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-鱼都在这里 -我们去抓
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.76,1:49:20.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-All the fish are over here. -Let's get them.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:27.27,1:49:29.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲,什么事情改变了你?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.27,1:49:29.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father, what changed you?
Dialogue: 1,1:49:31.69,1:49:33.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你确定我变了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.69,1:49:33.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I have?
Dialogue: 1,1:49:33.77,1:49:36.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的,你变了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.77,1:49:36.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. You changed.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:44.07,1:49:45.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.07,1:49:45.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:46.24,1:49:47.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.24,1:49:47.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It was your mother.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:52.62,1:49:55.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,女人对男人会有 很奇怪的影响力
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.62,1:49:55.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A woman can have a strange effect on a man.
Dialogue: 1,1:49:56.79,1:49:58.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,曾经...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.79,1:49:58.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There were times...
Dialogue: 1,1:49:59.09,1:50:01.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...在你妈身边 我连呼吸都有困难
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.09,1:50:01.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I had trouble breathing around your mother.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:02.59,1:50:04.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我了解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.59,1:50:04.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know the feeling.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:06.30,1:50:07.97,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你说过...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.30,1:50:07.97,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You once said...
Dialogue: 1,1:50:10.93,1:50:13.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...等我成家之后自然会明白
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.93,1:50:13.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...when I had a family of my own, l'd understand.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:17.44,1:50:18.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.44,1:50:18.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:21.57,1:50:23.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你想告诉我什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.57,1:50:23.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You're trying to tell me something.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:40.34,1:50:41.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-要吃苹果吗? -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.34,1:50:41.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Apple? -Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:48.76,1:50:49.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.76,1:50:49.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 1,1:50:50.14,1:50:51.85,对白中文,,0,0,0,,安派翠莎霍华...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.14,1:50:51.85,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Anne Patricia Howard...
Dialogue: 1,1:50:52.02,1:50:56.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你愿意嫁给此人为妻?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.02,1:50:56.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will you have this man to be your husband to live in marriage?
Dialogue: 1,1:50:56.52,1:50:59.15,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你会爱他,照顾他,荣显他...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.52,1:50:59.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Will you love, comfort and honor him...
Dialogue: 1,1:50:59.36,1:51:01.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...至死方休?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.36,1:51:01.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...for so long as you both shall live?
Dialogue: 1,1:51:02.15,1:51:03.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.15,1:51:03.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 1,1:51:03.90,1:51:07.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列艾德华马汀 你愿意娶此女为妻...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.90,1:51:07.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel Edward Martin, will you have this woman to be your wife...
Dialogue: 1,1:51:07.37,1:51:10.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...共同生活吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.37,1:51:10.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...to live together in the covenant of marriage?
Dialogue: 1,1:51:10.41,1:51:14.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你会爱她,安慰她,荣显她... 至死方休吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.41,1:51:14.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Will you love, comfort and honor her as long as you both shall live?
Dialogue: 1,1:51:14.79,1:51:15.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.79,1:51:15.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 1,1:51:16.04,1:51:18.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我依上帝...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.04,1:51:18.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Then by the power vested in me by our mutual faith...
Dialogue: 1,1:51:19.13,1:51:21.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...赋予我的权力...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.13,1:51:21.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...in the Lord, our God...
Dialogue: 1,1:51:21.30,1:51:24.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...宣布你们二人结为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.30,1:51:24.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I now pronounce you man and wife.
Dialogue: 1,1:51:51.70,1:51:54.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉没有早点告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.70,1:51:54.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we didn't give you more warning.
Dialogue: 1,1:51:54.20,1:51:55.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.20,1:51:55.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 1,1:51:55.79,1:51:57.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.79,1:51:57.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have something for you.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:00.00,1:52:01.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是佳百列他妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.00,1:52:01.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It belonged to Gabriel's mother.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:02.00,1:52:03.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.00,1:52:03.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:04.71,1:52:05.92,对白中文,,0,0,0,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.71,1:52:05.92,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:07.26,1:52:08.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是北极星
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.26,1:52:08.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's the North Star.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:09.30,1:52:12.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是天空中唯一不会动的星星
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.30,1:52:12.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's the only star in the sky that never moves.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:13.31,1:52:16.27,对白中文,,0,0,0,,它永远不会动摇
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.31,1:52:16.27,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's constant, unwavering.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:16.77,1:52:18.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为人指引方向
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.77,1:52:18.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A guide.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:21.65,1:52:23.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.65,1:52:23.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:28.49,1:52:29.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.49,1:52:29.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,May l?
Dialogue: 1,1:52:29.70,1:52:31.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-你坚持的话 -我坚持
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.70,1:52:31.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-lf you must. -I must.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:48.01,1:52:49.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我能坐在你身边吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.01,1:52:49.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,May I sit with you?
Dialogue: 1,1:52:49.80,1:52:51.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这是个自由的国家
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.80,1:52:51.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's a free country.
Dialogue: 1,1:52:52.55,1:52:53.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,至少以后会是
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.55,1:52:53.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Or at least it will be.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:06.23,1:53:08.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我不是我姐
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.23,1:53:08.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not my sister.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:09.36,1:53:11.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.36,1:53:11.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:11.70,1:53:13.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.70,1:53:13.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 1,1:53:14.49,1:53:15.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.49,1:53:15.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:17.04,1:53:18.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.04,1:53:18.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:23.25,1:53:24.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.25,1:53:24.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,1:53:26.00,1:53:27.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,什么怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.00,1:53:27.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Well what?
Dialogue: 1,1:53:49.49,1:53:51.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们很快就在潘布克见
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.49,1:53:51.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in Pembroke soon.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:51.53,1:53:53.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那不够快
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.53,1:53:53.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not soon enough.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:53.95,1:53:55.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我现在要靠你了...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.95,1:53:55.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to make sure...
Dialogue: 1,1:53:56.08,1:53:57.58,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我知道 -知道什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.08,1:53:57.58,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-I know. -What?
Dialogue: 1,1:53:57.79,1:53:59.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,帮我祷告,照顾每个人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.79,1:53:59.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Say my prayers, take care of everyone.
Dialogue: 1,1:53:59.79,1:54:01.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.79,1:54:01.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Couldn't have said it better.
Dialogue: 1,1:54:06.17,1:54:07.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.17,1:54:07.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 1,1:54:07.80,1:54:09.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.80,1:54:09.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 1,1:54:29.23,1:54:30.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见,苏珊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.23,1:54:30.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Susan.
Dialogue: 1,1:54:33.03,1:54:34.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,再见?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.03,1:54:34.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Goodbye?
Dialogue: 1,1:54:37.32,1:54:39.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我只要你说一句话就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.32,1:54:39.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Just one word, that's all I want.
Dialogue: 1,1:54:48.25,1:54:49.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.25,1:54:49.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:17.03,1:55:18.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.03,1:55:18.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 1,1:55:21.08,1:55:23.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸,别走!我什么都说
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.08,1:55:23.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Papa, don't go! I'll say anything.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:28.21,1:55:29.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,求求你,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.21,1:55:29.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Please, Papa.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:32.05,1:55:34.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你要我说什么,我就说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.05,1:55:34.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll say anything you want.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:34.30,1:55:37.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你要我说什么 我什么都说
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.30,1:55:37.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you want me to say. I'll say anything.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:40.30,1:55:43.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我保证,爸爸,不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.30,1:55:43.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I promise, Papa. Please don't go.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:44.23,1:55:45.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.23,1:55:45.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:46.44,1:55:47.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.44,1:55:47.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll come back.
Dialogue: 1,1:55:48.73,1:55:50.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会回来的,你相信我吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.73,1:55:50.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll come back. You believe me?
Dialogue: 1,1:55:54.19,1:55:56.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你让我非常快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.19,1:55:56.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You know, you make me very happy.
Dialogue: 1,1:56:32.19,1:56:33.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,只有我们三个?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.19,1:56:33.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Just the three of us?
Dialogue: 1,1:56:34.44,1:56:36.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,约翰蓝斯金来过
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.44,1:56:36.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,John Raskin did come by earlier.
Dialogue: 1,1:56:37.70,1:56:39.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他看了看就走了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.70,1:56:39.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He looked around, then he left.
Dialogue: 1,1:56:40.70,1:56:42.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那就四个人了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.70,1:56:42.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,He would've made four.
Dialogue: 1,1:56:42.53,1:56:44.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,四个人会比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.53,1:56:44.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Four would have been better.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:19.57,1:57:22.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我再撑两个月就满一年了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.57,1:57:22.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I got another two months to go before I get to twelve months.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:28.33,1:57:29.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.33,1:57:29.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:30.54,1:57:31.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,牧师
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.54,1:57:31.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Reverend.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:35.34,1:57:36.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,相信法国人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.34,1:57:36.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Trust the French.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:37.55,1:57:38.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是,相信法国人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.55,1:57:38.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, trust the French.
Dialogue: 1,1:57:39.01,1:57:42.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,还有什么其他机会 能杀红衫军?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.01,1:57:42.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where else do I get the opportunity to kill a few Redcoats?
Dialogue: 1,1:57:43.14,1:57:46.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,也许趁你不注意时 能杀几个受伤的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.14,1:57:46.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a few wounded ones when you are not looking.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:13.00,1:58:15.13,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大家都到教堂去集合
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.00,1:58:15.13,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Everyone must gather at the church.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:15.63,1:58:16.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,威尔金先生?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.63,1:58:16.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilkins?
Dialogue: 1,1:58:18.17,1:58:21.30,对白中文,,0,0,0,,塔维顿上校有话对村民说
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.17,1:58:21.30,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Colonel Tavington wishes to address the whole village.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:38.94,1:58:43.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,本镇人民帮助 班杰明马汀和他的叛党
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.94,1:58:43.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This town has given aid to Benjamin Martin and his rebels.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:43.61,1:58:45.45,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我要知道他的下落
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.61,1:58:45.45,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I wish to know his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:46.95,1:58:48.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.95,1:58:48.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 1,1:58:48.49,1:58:50.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...只要有人说出他的下落...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.49,1:58:50.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...anyone who comes forward...
Dialogue: 1,1:58:50.74,1:58:52.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我就饶了他的叛国罪
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.74,1:58:52.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...may be forgiven their treason.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:58.67,1:58:59.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.67,1:58:59.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 1,1:58:59.92,1:59:02.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-别说我没给过你们机会 -等等!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.92,1:59:02.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-You had your chance. -Wait!
Dialogue: 1,1:59:03.51,1:59:05.68,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-他给过他们补给品 -安静!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.51,1:59:05.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-This man gives them supplies. -Quiet!
Dialogue: 1,1:59:05.93,1:59:07.89,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-他带他们去黑沼泽 -他说谎!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.93,1:59:07.89,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-He brings them to Black Swamp. -Liar!
Dialogue: 1,1:59:08.10,1:59:10.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,就在西班牙教会旁的沼泽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.10,1:59:10.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,In the marsh, by the old Spanish mission.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:11.18,1:59:12.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.18,1:59:12.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This man here?
Dialogue: 1,1:59:12.77,1:59:14.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-是的 -你说黑沼泽?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.77,1:59:14.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Yes. -The Black Swamp, you say?
Dialogue: 1,1:59:15.10,1:59:17.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,就在西班牙教会旁的沼泽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.10,1:59:17.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,By the old Spanish mission.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:19.19,1:59:20.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.19,1:59:20.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:26.78,1:59:28.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把门关上
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.78,1:59:28.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Shut the doors.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:30.53,1:59:32.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你说会原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.53,1:59:32.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But you said we'd be forgiven.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:32.70,1:59:33.87,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你是会被原谅!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.70,1:59:33.87,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And indeed you may!
Dialogue: 1,1:59:36.71,1:59:38.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那是你和上帝之间的事
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.71,1:59:38.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That's between you and God.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:45.59,1:59:46.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们一定要坚强
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.59,1:59:46.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Be strong. We must.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:48.89,1:59:50.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们准备放火烧城了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.89,1:59:50.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll fire the town on your orders.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:50.76,1:59:52.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,烧城?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.76,1:59:52.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The town?
Dialogue: 1,1:59:52.89,1:59:54.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把教堂放火烧了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.89,1:59:54.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Burn the church.
Dialogue: 1,1:59:56.98,1:59:58.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这样做太不磊落
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.98,1:59:58.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,There's no honor in this.
Dialogue: 1,2:00:01.07,2:00:03.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你不是说任何背叛英国的人...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.07,2:00:03.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say all those who stand against England...
Dialogue: 1,2:00:04.07,2:00:06.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...都罪该万死吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.07,2:00:06.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...deserve to die a traitor's death?
Dialogue: 1,2:00:09.24,2:00:11.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,放火烧教堂
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.24,2:00:11.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Burn the church, captain.
Dialogue: 1,2:00:24.09,2:00:25.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,把火把拿来
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.09,2:00:25.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the torch.
Dialogue: 1,2:01:08.22,2:01:10.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,荣耀是来自结果而不是手段
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.22,2:01:10.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The honor is found in the end, not the means.
Dialogue: 1,2:01:12.05,2:01:13.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,这一切会被忘记的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.05,2:01:13.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,This will be forgotten.
Dialogue: 1,2:01:14.47,2:01:15.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,波顿
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.47,2:01:15.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Bordon.
Dialogue: 1,2:02:55.28,2:02:56.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,安!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.28,2:02:56.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 1,2:03:00.74,2:03:02.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,霍尔夫人?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.74,2:03:02.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Howard?
Dialogue: 1,2:03:06.58,2:03:08.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大家都到哪儿去了?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.58,2:03:08.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,2:03:13.34,2:03:15.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们不在这里
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.34,2:03:15.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 1,2:04:23.62,2:04:25.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列走了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.62,2:04:25.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel's gone.
Dialogue: 1,2:05:10.46,2:05:12.83,对白中文,,0,0,0,,快去拿武器...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.46,2:05:12.83,对白英文,,0,0,0,,To arms! To arms!
Dialogue: 1,2:09:32.47,2:09:33.76,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.47,2:09:33.76,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,2:09:35.14,2:09:37.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要讲话...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.14,2:09:37.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Just don't talk. Don't talk.
Dialogue: 1,2:09:43.81,2:09:44.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.81,2:09:44.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 1,2:09:45.44,2:09:47.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我很抱歉 -安静
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.44,2:09:47.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-l'm sorry. -Be quiet.
Dialogue: 1,2:09:47.86,2:09:49.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我会照顾你的 你不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.86,2:09:49.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you. You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 1,2:09:52.99,2:09:56.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,汤玛斯的事我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.99,2:09:56.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about Thomas.
Dialogue: 1,2:10:02.54,2:10:04.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,儿子,那不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.54,2:10:04.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, son, that wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 1,2:10:08.96,2:10:10.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.96,2:10:10.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,That was mine.
Dialogue: 1,2:10:14.55,2:10:17.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,忍着点,你不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.55,2:10:17.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hold on. You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 1,2:10:20.43,2:10:23.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要死,佳百列
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.43,2:10:23.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Don't go. Gabriel, don't.
Dialogue: 1,2:10:52.38,2:10:54.72,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上帝,帮帮我...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.38,2:10:54.72,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, God help me. God help me.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:28.75,2:11:30.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.75,2:11:30.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 1,2:11:38.01,2:11:39.93,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我来帮你埋了他
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.01,2:11:39.93,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll help you bury him.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:42.10,2:11:43.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.10,2:11:43.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'll bury him.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:46.69,2:11:49.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我太太怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.69,2:11:49.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My wife in Alexandria is with child.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:50.94,2:11:52.61,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是我们的第一胎
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.94,2:11:52.61,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My first.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:53.28,2:11:55.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我为那孩子作战
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.28,2:11:55.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I fight for that child.
Dialogue: 1,2:11:57.78,2:12:00.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明,没有人能取代你儿子
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.78,2:12:00.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin, nothing will replace your sons.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:01.62,2:12:05.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但如果你跟我们来 他们就不会白死
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.62,2:12:05.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But if you come with us, you can justify their sacrifice.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:07.62,2:12:09.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.62,2:12:09.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,2:12:10.79,2:12:14.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为何你们会觉得他们不会白死
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.79,2:12:14.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Why do men feel they can justify death?
Dialogue: 1,2:12:21.39,2:12:23.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,是傲慢还是...?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.39,2:12:23.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Is it arrogance or...?
Dialogue: 1,2:12:27.98,2:12:29.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我长久以来的恐惧...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.98,2:12:29.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have long feared...
Dialogue: 1,2:12:31.69,2:12:35.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...就是我旧日的罪孽 会回来纠缠我
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.69,2:12:35.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...that my sins would return to visit me.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:38.20,2:12:40.82,对白中文,,0,0,0,,代价之高,我无法承受
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.20,2:12:40.82,对白英文,,0,0,0,,And the cost is more than I can bear.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:42.16,2:12:46.00,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班杰明,我们有机会
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.16,2:12:46.00,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Benjamin, we have a chance.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:46.54,2:12:49.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,葛林和丹摩根从维吉尼亚来了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.54,2:12:49.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Greene and Dan Morgan are down from Virginia.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:52.42,2:12:56.01,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们打赢下一战 就胜利在望了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.42,2:12:56.01,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If we win this next battle, victory in the war is within our grasp.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:56.21,2:12:57.22,对白中文,,0,0,0,,那么,去吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.21,2:12:57.22,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Go, then.
Dialogue: 1,2:12:57.51,2:12:59.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,去追求你们的胜利
Dialogue: 0,2:12:57.51,2:12:59.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Seek your victory.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:02.68,2:13:05.77,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-我不重要 -你错了,班杰明
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.68,2:13:05.77,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-l'm small issue to it. -You're wrong, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:06.52,2:13:08.52,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你对你的手下...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.52,2:13:08.52,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You matter to your men...
Dialogue: 1,2:13:10.02,2:13:11.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...和对其他人都很重要
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.02,2:13:11.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and to others as well.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:12.36,2:13:14.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你的胜利...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.36,2:13:14.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your victories...
Dialogue: 1,2:13:14.36,2:13:16.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...和失去的...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:14.36,2:13:16.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and your losses...
Dialogue: 1,2:13:17.53,2:13:19.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...大家都感同身受
Dialogue: 0,2:13:17.53,2:13:19.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...are shared by more than you know.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:20.86,2:13:23.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,和我们一起吧
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.86,2:13:23.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stay with us.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:23.53,2:13:25.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,为自由而战
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.53,2:13:25.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Stay the course.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:35.21,2:13:37.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我已经为我的理由奋斗过了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.21,2:13:37.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I have run my course.
Dialogue: 1,2:13:57.40,2:13:59.86,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你的手下跟我们走
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.40,2:13:59.86,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You men will be leaving with us.
Dialogue: 1,2:14:02.74,2:14:04.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,准备出发
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.74,2:14:04.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Prepare the baggage.
Dialogue: 1,2:15:08.81,2:15:09.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,尚
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.81,2:15:09.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Jean.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:02.94,2:16:06.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,明天的战役将会改变整场战事
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.94,2:16:06.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's battle can alter the course of the war.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:06.36,2:16:09.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,葛林将军 我们究竟会遭遇何种情况?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.36,2:16:09.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,General Greene, what exactly is the task before us?
Dialogue: 1,2:16:09.53,2:16:12.62,对白中文,,0,0,0,,各位,我们被康瓦理斯包围了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.53,2:16:12.62,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, Cornwallis has us cornered.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:13.29,2:16:15.04,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他的人数比我们多
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.29,2:16:15.04,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Not only does he outnumber us...
Dialogue: 1,2:16:15.25,2:16:18.29,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的手下几乎全是民兵
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.25,2:16:18.29,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...but nearly half of our force is militia.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:19.58,2:16:21.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们靠不住
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.58,2:16:21.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Unreliable, at best.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:22.25,2:16:24.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,对不起,长官
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.25,2:16:24.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:25.76,2:16:27.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你低估了我们的民兵
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.76,2:16:27.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You underestimate our militia.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:29.76,2:16:31.10,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你们都一样
Dialogue: 0,2:16:29.76,2:16:31.10,对白英文,,0,0,0,,All of you do.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:31.93,2:16:34.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们看过民兵的防线 一而再,再而三的被击溃
Dialogue: 0,2:16:31.93,2:16:34.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We've seen our militia lines break time and again.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:34.81,2:16:36.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,克比斯湾,普林斯顿
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.81,2:16:36.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Kips Bay, Princeton.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:36.77,2:16:38.90,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但英国人也这么想
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.77,2:16:38.90,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But the British have seen that too.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:39.81,2:16:43.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,康瓦理斯的信中 完全看不起民兵
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.81,2:16:43.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Cornwallis' own letters bear out that he has no respect for the militia.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:44.32,2:16:46.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你有何建议?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.32,2:16:46.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What are you suggesting, Ben?
Dialogue: 1,2:16:48.07,2:16:49.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我建议我们利用这点
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.07,2:16:49.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm suggesting we use that.
Dialogue: 1,2:16:57.16,2:17:01.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你们已经牺牲了很多
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.16,2:17:01.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know you men have sacrificed a lot so far.
Dialogue: 1,2:17:01.38,2:17:04.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,但我只要求你们...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.38,2:17:04.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But all l'm asking is that you...
Dialogue: 1,2:17:05.00,2:17:08.17,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...让前两排的民兵开两枪
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.00,2:17:08.17,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...Iet the front line of the militia fire two shots tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,2:17:10.34,2:17:13.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,发射两轮子弹的期间 可能会发生很多事
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.34,2:17:13.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,A lot can happen in the time it takes to fire two shots.
Dialogue: 1,2:17:13.68,2:17:16.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,特别是在对抗英国正规军时
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.68,2:17:16.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Especially against British Regulars.
Dialogue: 1,2:17:17.18,2:17:20.94,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没错 所以我才不叫你们开三枪
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.18,2:17:20.94,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Indeed. That's why l'm not asking you to fire three.
Dialogue: 1,2:18:18.08,2:18:20.41,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果我死的话,至少死得体面
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.08,2:18:20.41,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If I die, I will die well-dressed.
Dialogue: 1,2:19:06.63,2:19:07.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.63,2:19:07.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,2:19:11.63,2:19:14.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-大队! -停!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.63,2:19:14.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Battalion! -Company, halt!
Dialogue: 1,2:19:31.57,2:19:32.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,哈利...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:31.57,2:19:32.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Harry...
Dialogue: 1,2:19:33.65,2:19:35.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...麻烦把这给我的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.65,2:19:35.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will you give this to my children?
Dialogue: 1,2:19:46.12,2:19:47.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.12,2:19:47.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,2:19:56.51,2:19:58.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在是十月
Dialogue: 0,2:19:56.51,2:19:58.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's October now.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:00.85,2:20:02.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,2:20:00.85,2:20:02.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:02.89,2:20:04.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在已经超过十二个月了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.89,2:20:04.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It's more than 12 months.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:05.31,2:20:06.60,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你自由了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:05.31,2:20:06.60,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You're a free man.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:07.77,2:20:10.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我自愿留下来
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.77,2:20:10.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm here now on my own accord.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:14.40,2:20:16.49,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你愿留下来我很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.40,2:20:16.49,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to have you with us.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:18.82,2:20:20.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,真的很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.82,2:20:20.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Honored.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:21.66,2:20:24.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,举枪!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:21.66,2:20:24.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Shoulder arms!
Dialogue: 1,2:20:29.92,2:20:31.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,前进...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.92,2:20:31.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Forward...
Dialogue: 1,2:20:32.34,2:20:33.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...齐步走!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.34,2:20:33.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...march!
Dialogue: 1,2:20:38.63,2:20:40.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你女儿几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.63,2:20:40.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How old were your daughters?
Dialogue: 1,2:20:42.51,2:20:45.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,维尔莉特十二,宝琳十岁
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.51,2:20:45.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Violette was 12 and Pauline, 10.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:46.18,2:20:48.14,对白中文,,0,0,0,,他们的眼睛都是绿的
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.18,2:20:48.14,对白英文,,0,0,0,,They had green eyes.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:49.44,2:20:51.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她们一定很可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.44,2:20:51.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they were lovely.
Dialogue: 1,2:20:52.82,2:20:54.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.82,2:20:54.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, they were.
Dialogue: 1,2:21:06.33,2:21:07.54,对白中文,,0,0,0,,-大队! -注意!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.33,2:21:07.54,对白英文,,0,0,0,,-Battalion! -Company!
Dialogue: 1,2:21:07.96,2:21:09.12,对白中文,,0,0,0,,齐步走!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.96,2:21:09.12,对白英文,,0,0,0,,March!
Dialogue: 1,2:21:11.33,2:21:12.59,对白中文,,0,0,0,,瞄准!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.33,2:21:12.59,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 1,2:21:15.38,2:21:16.63,对白中文,,0,0,0,,除非我在做梦...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.38,2:21:16.63,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Unless l'm dreaming...
Dialogue: 1,2:21:17.34,2:21:21.34,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我好像看到 他们的队伍中央居然是民兵
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.34,2:21:21.34,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I believe I see militia forming at their center.
Dialogue: 1,2:21:35.69,2:21:38.07,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大队!停!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.69,2:21:38.07,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Battalion, halt!
Dialogue: 1,2:21:56.21,2:21:58.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,第一排向前!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.21,2:21:58.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dress ranks!
