Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.02,2:23:40.15,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 1,2:23:46.20,2:23:50.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,上刺刀,看看鹿死谁手
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.20,2:23:50.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Bayonet charge. We'll see who takes the glory from this field.
Dialogue: 1,2:23:50.53,2:23:52.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,进攻!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.53,2:23:52.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 1,2:24:12.06,2:24:13.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,恭喜你,大人
Dialogue: 0,2:24:12.06,2:24:13.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, my lord.
Dialogue: 1,2:24:13.85,2:24:15.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,叫步兵储备军过来
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.85,2:24:15.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Infantry reserve into the center.
Dialogue: 1,2:24:15.52,2:24:16.81,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经占领了此地
Dialogue: 0,2:24:15.52,2:24:16.81,对白英文,,0,0,0,,But you've taken the field.
Dialogue: 1,2:24:17.02,2:24:18.40,对白中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们要打垮他们的士气
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.02,2:24:18.40,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Now we'll take their spirits.
Dialogue: 1,2:24:18.60,2:24:21.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,叫我们的士兵去击溃他们
Dialogue: 0,2:24:18.60,2:24:21.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Send the battalion over that hill and crush them.
Dialogue: 1,2:24:21.86,2:24:23.28,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战争今天就要结束
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.86,2:24:23.28,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It ends today.
