Dialogue: 1,2:26:41.00,2:26:42.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们的军队要瓦解了!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:41.00,2:26:42.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The line is faltering!
Dialogue: 1,2:26:43.92,2:26:46.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,撤退...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.92,2:26:46.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
