Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.30,2:26:55.68,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 1,2:26:56.51,2:26:58.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,不要撤退!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:56.51,2:26:58.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,No retreat!
Dialogue: 1,2:27:02.02,2:27:04.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,保持队形!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:02.02,2:27:04.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hold the line!
Dialogue: 1,2:27:05.90,2:27:08.02,对白中文,,0,0,0,,保持队形!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:05.90,2:27:08.02,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Hold the line!
Dialogue: 1,2:27:19.70,2:27:22.79,对白中文,,0,0,0,,推进!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.70,2:27:22.79,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Push forward, men!
Dialogue: 1,2:28:12.25,2:28:14.55,对白中文,,0,0,0,,叫炮兵到中间集合
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.25,2:28:14.55,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Artillery, concentrate on the center.
Dialogue: 1,2:28:29.77,2:28:33.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们重新整队 朝右前进,也许能逼他们撤退
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.77,2:28:33.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,If we reform and wheel right, we may be able to turn their flank.
Dialogue: 1,2:28:33.73,2:28:35.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你想得美,将军
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.73,2:28:35.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You dream, general.
Dialogue: 1,2:31:38.17,2:31:40.75,对白中文,,0,0,0,,拜托你在战争结束之前杀了我
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.17,2:31:40.75,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Kill me before the war is over, will you?
Dialogue: 1,2:31:42.42,2:31:45.09,对白中文,,0,0,0,,看来你...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:42.42,2:31:45.09,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It appears you are not...
Dialogue: 1,2:31:45.30,2:31:47.47,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...还是不如我
Dialogue: 0,2:31:45.30,2:31:47.47,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...the better man.
Dialogue: 1,2:32:01.23,2:32:02.23,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,2:32:01.23,2:32:02.23,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 1,2:32:07.03,2:32:09.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我的儿子比你好多了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:07.03,2:32:09.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My sons were better men.
Dialogue: 1,2:32:36.85,2:32:38.35,对白中文,,0,0,0,,叫他们撤退
Dialogue: 0,2:32:36.85,2:32:38.35,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sound the retreat.
Dialogue: 1,2:32:41.90,2:32:43.36,对白中文,,0,0,0,,叫他们...
Dialogue: 0,2:32:41.90,2:32:43.36,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sound...
Dialogue: 1,2:32:44.48,2:32:45.69,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...撤退
Dialogue: 0,2:32:44.48,2:32:45.69,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...retreat.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:03.71,2:33:04.71,对白中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的夏绿蒂：
Dialogue: 0,2:33:03.71,2:33:04.71,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Charlotte:
Dialogue: 1,2:33:05.51,2:33:07.26,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战事已经改观
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.51,2:33:07.26,对白英文,,0,0,0,,The war has turned.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:07.47,2:33:11.05,对白中文,,0,0,0,,康瓦理斯将军带着手下 逃向北方
Dialogue: 0,2:33:07.47,2:33:11.05,对白英文,,0,0,0,,General Cornwallis took flight with his army and moved north.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:11.39,2:33:14.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们持续与英军交战 在未来数月间...
Dialogue: 0,2:33:11.39,2:33:14.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We continued to engage the British, and in the following months...
Dialogue: 1,2:33:14.51,2:33:17.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...康瓦理斯会被困在 维吉尼亚州,约克镇
Dialogue: 0,2:33:14.51,2:33:17.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...Cornwallis entrenched himself at Yorktown, Virginia.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:18.19,2:33:19.48,注解,,0,0,0,,约克镇, 1781年
Dialogue: 1,2:33:19.64,2:33:21.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,乔治·华盛顿悄悄地突围到北方
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.64,2:33:21.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Washington escaped from the north...
Dialogue: 1,2:33:21.73,2:33:24.98,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...包围了康瓦理斯 他无法撤退至海上
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.73,2:33:24.98,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and surrounded Cornwallis, who could not retreat to the seas.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:25.32,2:33:28.53,对白中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们期待已久的朋友 终于抵达...
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.32,2:33:28.53,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It was blocked off by our long-lost friends...
Dialogue: 1,2:33:28.74,2:33:31.24,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...挡住他的去路
Dialogue: 0,2:33:28.74,2:33:31.24,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...who had finally arrived.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:35.79,2:33:37.20,对白中文,,0,0,0,,法国万岁
Dialogue: 0,2:33:35.79,2:33:37.20,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Vive la France.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:39.92,2:33:41.50,对白中文,,0,0,0,,自由万岁
Dialogue: 0,2:33:39.92,2:33:41.50,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Vive la liberte.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:53.64,2:33:55.56,对白中文,,0,0,0,,大人,我求你
Dialogue: 0,2:33:53.64,2:33:55.56,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My lord, I beseech you.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:56.18,2:33:58.43,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你一定要下令投降
Dialogue: 0,2:33:56.18,2:33:58.43,对白英文,,0,0,0,,You must order the surrender.
Dialogue: 1,2:33:59.27,2:34:02.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会变成这样? 他们只是杂牌军
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.27,2:34:02.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,How could it come to this? An army of rabble.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:03.06,2:34:04.48,对白中文,,0,0,0,,庄稼汉
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.06,2:34:04.48,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Peasants.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:06.69,2:34:08.65,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会不同
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.69,2:34:08.65,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Everything will change.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:12.16,2:34:14.16,对白中文,,0,0,0,,一切都不同了
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.16,2:34:14.16,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Everything has changed.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:14.95,2:34:16.99,对白中文,,0,0,0,,虽然他终于还是投降了...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:14.95,2:34:16.99,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Though he eventually surrendered...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:17.20,2:34:19.66,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...但康瓦理斯无脸见人...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.20,2:34:19.66,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...Cornwallis himself hid in shame...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:19.87,2:34:23.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...派他的手下前来投降
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.87,2:34:23.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...appointing his subordinate to relinquish his sword.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:24.67,2:34:27.80,对白中文,,0,0,0,,战争就要结束 民兵团即将解散...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:24.67,2:34:27.80,对白英文,,0,0,0,,With the war ending, and our militia disbanding...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:28.00,2:34:30.67,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我回顾我们所失去的...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:28.00,2:34:30.67,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...I take measure of what we have lost...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:30.88,2:34:32.38,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...及我们得到的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:30.88,2:34:32.38,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...and what we have won.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:33.55,2:34:38.31,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我希望这么多人的牺牲...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:33.55,2:34:38.31,对白英文,,0,0,0,,My hope and prayer is that the sacrifices borne by so many...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:38.52,2:34:42.39,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...能够让我们的新国家诞生
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.52,2:34:42.39,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...will spawn and fulfill the promise of our new nation.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:43.77,2:34:47.73,对白中文,,0,0,0,,告诉孩子们,尤其要告诉苏珊 我会遵守诺言...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.77,2:34:47.73,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Tell the children, and especially Susan, that I will keep my promise...
Dialogue: 1,2:34:47.94,2:34:51.57,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我很快就会回到你们身边
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.94,2:34:51.57,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...as I will be returning to you all soon.
Dialogue: 1,2:34:57.66,2:34:59.33,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:57.66,2:34:59.33,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Where will you go now?
Dialogue: 1,2:35:00.12,2:35:02.37,对白中文,,0,0,0,,回家,从头开始
Dialogue: 0,2:35:00.12,2:35:02.37,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Home. Start over.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:02.62,2:35:04.96,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你太太就快生了,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:02.62,2:35:04.96,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Your wife's expecting a child, isn't she?
Dialogue: 1,2:35:05.17,2:35:07.88,对白中文,,0,0,0,,她三周前生了个儿子
Dialogue: 0,2:35:05.17,2:35:07.88,对白英文,,0,0,0,,She gave birth to a son three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:09.05,2:35:10.46,对白中文,,0,0,0,,你帮他取什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:09.05,2:35:10.46,对白英文,,0,0,0,,What'd you name him?
Dialogue: 1,2:35:12.55,2:35:14.51,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我们叫他佳百列
Dialogue: 0,2:35:12.55,2:35:14.51,对白英文,,0,0,0,,We named him Gabriel.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:20.14,2:35:21.18,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢,哈利
Dialogue: 0,2:35:20.14,2:35:21.18,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Harry.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:28.40,2:35:31.11,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列是个适合农夫的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:35:28.40,2:35:31.11,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel is a good name for a farmer.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:31.61,2:35:34.03,对白中文,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,2:35:31.61,2:35:34.03,对白英文,,0,0,0,,It is. It is.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:34.57,2:35:35.70,对白中文,,0,0,0,,尚
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.57,2:35:35.70,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Jean.
Dialogue: 1,2:35:35.91,2:35:36.91,对白中文,,0,0,0,,班
Dialogue: 0,2:35:35.91,2:35:36.91,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Ben.
Dialogue: 1,2:36:44.39,2:36:47.06,对白中文,,0,0,0,,佳百列说如果我们打赢的话...
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.39,2:36:47.06,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Gabriel said if we won the war...
Dialogue: 1,2:36:47.48,2:36:49.44,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...我们会建立一个全新的世界
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.48,2:36:49.44,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...we could build a whole new world.
Dialogue: 1,2:36:50.44,2:36:53.19,对白中文,,0,0,0,,我想我们就从这里开始...
Dialogue: 0,2:36:50.44,2:36:53.19,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Just figured we'd get started right here...
Dialogue: 1,2:36:54.61,2:36:56.32,对白中文,,0,0,0,,...从你们的家开始
Dialogue: 0,2:36:54.61,2:36:56.32,对白英文,,0,0,0,,...with your home.
Dialogue: 1,2:37:00.32,2:37:01.78,对白中文,,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,2:37:00.32,2:37:01.78,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 1,2:37:05.25,2:37:06.25,对白中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:37:05.25,2:37:06.25,对白英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.

